  <para style="h">UMakho</para>
  <para style="toc1">Ivangeli LikaMakho</para>
  <para style="toc2">UMakho</para>
  <para style="toc3">Mak</para>
  <para style="mt2">Ivangeli</para>
  <para style="mt1">LikaMakho</para>
  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">UMakho ukhanya wabhalelwa abantu baseRoma. Amazwi akhulunywa yinduna yekhulu yaseRoma ekucineni kwebhuku, <char style="qt">Ngempela lindoda ibiyindodana kaNkulunkulu</char>, alungiselela lowo ofakazayo kuJesu.</para>
  <para style="ip">Ingxenye yakuqala yalindaba igxile embuzweni: <char style="qt">Lithi ngingubani?</char> Ekupheleni kwengxenye yakuqala kuba lesehlakalo, uJesu usilisa indoda engaboniyo ezigabeni ezimbili lokho okwenza waqala ukubona kancanekancane. Ngokufanayo abalandeli bakaJesu baqala ukunanzelela ukuthi uJesu ungubani. Esikhathini esiqakathekileyo endabeni phakathi kwengxenye ezimbili uPhethro nguye ovumayo ukuthi uJesu nguKhristu.</para>
  <para style="ip">Ukungazwanani lokhu sokusuka kube segcekeni. UJesu usebuye lendlela entsha yokuphila eqakathekileyo ezokuthi ilungisise ubuthungameli obukhona obamandla. Ingxenye yesibili yalindaba iyakuveza lokho ezehlakalweni ezintathu.</para>
  <para style="ili1">Okokuqala, uJesu labafundi bakhe baya eJerusalema.</para>
  <para style="ili1">Okulandelayo, uJesu ufundisa ethempelini, uxabana lobuthungameli obuvele bukhona.</para>
  <para style="ili1">Esahlukweni sokucina lobo buthungameli buqhuba icebo labo, babophisa uJesu bamenza abethelwe esiphambanweni, bakutshaya indiva konke akwenzayo. Kodwa uNkulunkulu uyakutshintsha lokho uvusa uJesu kwabafileyo. Ngokunjalo ababali bakaMakho bakhuthazwa ukuthi bebengamakholwa athembekileyo, lasekudubekeni ngoba le yindlela uNkulunkulu aqhubeka ngayo entshintsha lokho okukhona ekhuthaza indlela yokuphila uJesu ayifundisayo.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="MRK 1"/>
  <para style="s1">UJohane Umbhaphathizi Ulungisa Indlela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 1:1"/>Ukuqala kwevangeli ngoJesu Khristu, indodana kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="MRK 1:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 1:2"/>Kulotshiwe kumphrofethi u-Isaya ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 1:2">“Ngizathuma isithunywa sami phambi kwakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 1:2">esizalungisa indlela yakho”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UMalaki 3.1</char></note>:<verse eid="MRK 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 1:3"/>“ilizwi lalowo omemezayo enkangala,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 1:3">‘Lungiselani iNkosi indlela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 1:3">yenzeleni izindledlana eziqondileyo.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 40.3</char></note>”<verse eid="MRK 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 1:4"/>Kwasekufika uJohane Umbhaphathizi, etshumayela emangweni wasenkangala ubhaphathizo lokuphenduka ukuze kuthethelelwe izono. <verse eid="MRK 1:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 1:5"/>Umango wonke waseJudiya kanye labantu bonke baseJerusalema baphuma baya kuye. Bevuma izono zabo, babhaphathizwa nguye eMfuleni uJodani. <verse eid="MRK 1:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 1:6"/>UJohane wayevunula izigqoko ezazenziwe ngoboya bekamela, elebhanti lesikhumba okhalweni lwakhe, esidla intethe loluju lwezinyosi zeganga. <verse eid="MRK 1:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 1:7"/>Intshumayelo yakhe yayisithi: “Ngemva kwami kuzafika omunye ozaba lamandla kulami, imichilo yamanyathela akhe akungilingananga ukuthi ngikhothame ngiyithukulule. <verse eid="MRK 1:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 1:8"/>Mina ngilibhaphathiza ngamanzi, kodwa yena uzalibhaphathiza ngoMoya oNgcwele.”<verse eid="MRK 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubhaphathizwa Lokulingwa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 1:9"/>Ngalesosikhathi uJesu weza evela eNazaretha eseGalile wabhaphathizwa nguJohane kuJodani. <verse eid="MRK 1:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 1:10"/>UJesu ephuma emanzini wabona izulu livuleka uMoya usehlela phezu kwakhe unjengejuba. <verse eid="MRK 1:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 1:11"/>Kwafika ilizwi livela ezulwini lathi: “Wena uyiNdodana yami engiyithandayo; ngiyathokoza kakhulu ngawe.”<verse eid="MRK 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 1:12"/>Masinyane uMoya wamthumela enkangala, <verse eid="MRK 1:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 1:13"/>wahlala khona enkangala insuku ezingamatshumi amane elingwa nguSathane. Wayehlala lezinyamazana zeganga, izingilosi zazomnakekela.<verse eid="MRK 1:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uqala Ukutshumayela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 1:14"/>UJohane esevalelwe entolongweni, uJesu waya eGalile ememezela izindaba ezinhle zikaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="MRK 1:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 1:15"/>Wathi, <char style="wj">“Isikhathi sesifikile. Umbuso kaNkulunkulu ususeduze. Phendukani likholwe izindaba ezinhle!”</char><verse eid="MRK 1:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubizwa Kwabafundi Bokuqala</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 1:16"/>Kwathi uJesu ehambahamba okhunjini loLwandle lwaseGalile wabona uSimoni lomfowabo u-Andreya bephosa umambule olwandle ngoba babengabagoli benhlanzi. <verse eid="MRK 1:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 1:17"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Wozani lingilandele, ngizalenza abagoli babantu.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 1:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 1:18"/>Bahle batshiya omambule babo bamlandela.<verse eid="MRK 1:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 1:19"/>Wathi esehambile elinye ibanga wabona uJakhobe indodana kaZebhediya elomfowabo uJohane besesikepeni, belungisa omambule babo. <verse eid="MRK 1:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 1:20"/>Wahle wababiza, batshiya uyise uZebhediya esikepeni kanye lezisebenzi bamlandela.<verse eid="MRK 1:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ukhupha Umoya Omubi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 1:21"/>Baya eKhaphenawume, kwathi iSabatha selifikile, uJesu waya esinagogeni waqalisa ukufundisa. <verse eid="MRK 1:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 1:22"/>Abantu bamangaliswa yikufundisa kwakhe ngoba wayefundisa njengomuntu olamandla, hatshi njengabafundisi bomthetho. <verse eid="MRK 1:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 1:23"/>Khonokho nje indoda eyayisesinagogeni labo eyayiphethwe ngumoya omubi yamemeza yathi, <verse eid="MRK 1:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 1:24"/>“Ufunani kithi, Jesu waseNazaretha? Ulande ukuza sibhubhisa na? Ngiyakwazi ukuthi ungubani, ungoNgcwele kaNkulunkulu!”<verse eid="MRK 1:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 1:25"/>UJesu wakhwaza wathi kuye <char style="wj">“Thula! Phuma kuye!”</char> <verse eid="MRK 1:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 1:26"/>Umoya omubi wayidlukuza ngamandla indoda waphuma kuyo uklabalala.<verse eid="MRK 1:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 1:27"/>Abantu bamangala baze babuzana bathi, “Kuyini lokhu? Yikufundisa okutsha njalo okulamandla! Ngoba ulaya imimoya emibi imlalele.” <verse eid="MRK 1:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 1:28"/>Izindaba ngaye zamemetheka ngokuphangisa kuwo wonke umango waseGalile.<verse eid="MRK 1:28"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usilisa Abanengi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 1:29"/>Bonela ukusuka esinagogeni bahamba loJakhobe loJohane baya emzini kaSimoni lo-Andreya. <verse eid="MRK 1:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 1:30"/>Uninazala kaSimoni wayelele phansi ephethwe ngumkhuhlane, basebetshela uJesu ngaye. <verse eid="MRK 1:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 1:31"/>Ngakho wasesiya kuye, wambamba isandla wasemvusa. Umkhuhlane waphuma kuye, wahle waqalisa ukubaphakela.<verse eid="MRK 1:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 1:32"/>Ngaleyontambama ilanga selitshonile abantu baletha kuJesu bonke abagulayo labaphethwe ngamadimoni. <verse eid="MRK 1:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 1:33"/>Idolobho lonke lagcwala emnyango, <verse eid="MRK 1:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 1:34"/>uJesu wasilisa abanengi ababelezifo ezehlukeneyo. Njalo wakhupha amadimoni amanengi, kodwa kaze awavumela amadimoni ukuthi akhulume ngoba ayemazi ukuthi ungubani.<verse eid="MRK 1:34"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ukhuleka Ekusithekeni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 1:35"/>Ekuseni kakhulu, kusesempondozankomo, uJesu wavuka, waphuma endlini waya endaweni esekusithekeni, lapho akhuleka khona. <verse eid="MRK 1:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 1:36"/>USimoni labakhula bakhe bahamba ukuyamdinga, <verse eid="MRK 1:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 1:37"/>sebembonile, bathi, “Abantu bonke bayakudinga!”<verse eid="MRK 1:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 1:38"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kasiyeni kwenye indawo, emizini eseduze ukuze ngiyetshumayela lakhona. Yikho engakulandayo.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 1:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 1:39"/>Kanjalo walibhoda lonke elaseGalile etshumayela emasinagogweni abo njalo ekhupha amadimoni.<verse eid="MRK 1:39"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usilisa Indoda Elobulephero</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 1:40"/>Kweza kuye indoda eyayilobulephero yamncenga iguqe phansi ngamadolo yathi, “Nxa uthanda ungangihlambulula.”<verse eid="MRK 1:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 1:41"/>UJesu eyizwela isihawu welula isandla sakhe wayibamba indoda. Wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngiyathanda. Hlanzeka!”</char> <verse eid="MRK 1:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 1:42"/>Masinyane ubulephero baphela, wahlambuluka.<verse eid="MRK 1:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="MRK 1:43"/>UJesu wahle wathi kahambe, wamqonqosela wathi, <verse eid="MRK 1:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MRK 1:44"/><char style="wj">“Zwana, ungatsheli muntu ngalokhu. Kodwa hamba uyeziveza kumphristi ubusunikela umhlatshelo wokuhlanjululwa kwakho owamiswa nguMosi ukuze kube yibufakazi kubo.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 1:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="MRK 1:45"/>Kodwa wasuka wahle wavula isifuba sakhe wayisakaza indaba. Ngenxa yalokho uJesu wayengabe esangena obala edolobheni, kodwa wasehlala ngaphandle endaweni eziyinkangala. Loba kunjalo abantu babelokhu bethululeka besiza kuye beqhamuka inxa zonke.<verse eid="MRK 1:45"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="MRK 2"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usilisa Umuntu Oyisilima</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 2:1"/>Ngemva kwezinsukwana, uJesu esengenile njalo eKhaphenawume, abantu bezwa ukuthi wayesebuyile ekhaya. <verse eid="MRK 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 2:2"/>Bathi cwi ndawonye kwaze kwasweleka indawo langasemnyango, watshumayela ilizwi kubo. <verse eid="MRK 2:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 2:3"/>Kwafika amadoda amane ethwele eyayome umhlubulo. <verse eid="MRK 2:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 2:4"/>Kwathi ngoba bengafinyeleli kuJesu ngenxa yexuku, bavula isikhala ephahleni malungana loJesu, emva kokuphendla ngaso, behlisela umendlalo owawulele indoda eyome umhlubulo. <verse eid="MRK 2:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 2:5"/>Kwathi uJesu ebona ukholo lwawo wathi endodeni eyome umhlubulo, <char style="wj">“Ndodana, izono zakho sezithethelelwe.”</char><verse eid="MRK 2:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 2:6"/>Khonapho kwakuhlezi abanye abafundisi bomthetho, benakana besithi, <verse eid="MRK 2:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 2:7"/>“Umuntu lo ukhulumeleni kanjalo? Uyahlambaza! Ngubani ongathethelela izono ngaphandle kukaNkulunkulu yedwa?”<verse eid="MRK 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 2:8"/>Masinyane uJesu wakwazi emoyeni wakhe ukuthi yilokho ababekucabanga ezinhliziyweni zabo, wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Kungani linakana izinto ezinje ezinhliziyweni zenu?</char> <verse eid="MRK 2:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 2:9"/><char style="wj">Yikuphi okulula: ukuthi kowome umhlubulo: ‘Izono zakho sezithethelelwe,’ loba ukuthi, ‘Phakama, thatha icansi lakho uhambe’?</char> <verse eid="MRK 2:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 2:10"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ukuze lazi ukuthi iNdodana yoMuntu ilamandla emhlabeni ukuthethelela izono.”</char> Wathi kowome umhlubulo, <verse eid="MRK 2:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 2:11"/><char style="wj">“Ngiyakutshela, phakama, thatha icansi lakho uye ekhaya.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 2:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 2:12"/>Waphakama wathatha icansi lakhe waphuma wahamba bonke bemkhangele. Lokho kwamangalisa umuntu wonke, bamdumisa uNkulunkulu besithi, “Kasikaze sikubone okunje!”<verse eid="MRK 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubizwa KukaLevi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 2:13"/>UJesu waphinde wayahambahamba eduzane lechibi. Ixuku elikhulu labantu leza kuye, wasebafundisa. <verse eid="MRK 2:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 2:14"/>Wathi elokhu ehambahamba wabona uLevi indodana ka-Alifewu ihlezi endaweni yokuthelisa. UJesu wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Ngilandela,”</char> ULevi wasukuma wamlandela.<verse eid="MRK 2:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 2:15"/>Kwathi uJesu esidla okwakusihlwa endlini kaLevi kwakulabathelisi abanengi “lezoni” zisidla laye kanye labafundi bakhe, ngoba babebanengi ababemlandela. <verse eid="MRK 2:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 2:16"/>Kuthe abafundisi bomthetho ababe ngabaFarisi bembona esidla “lezoni” labathelisi babuza abafundi bakhe bathi, “Wenzelani ukudla labathelisi kanye ‘lezoni’?”<verse eid="MRK 2:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 2:17"/>Wathi ekuzwa lokho uJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Abaphilayo kabamdingi umelaphi, kodwa abagulayo bayamdinga. Kangilandanga ukuzobiza abalungileyo, kodwa izoni.”</char><verse eid="MRK 2:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ubuzwa Ngokuzila</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 2:18"/>Ngalesosikhathi abafundi bakaJohane labaFarisi babezila. Abanye abantu beza babuza uJesu bathi, “Kungani abafundi bakaJohane labafundi babaFarisi bezila, kodwa abakho kabazili?”<verse eid="MRK 2:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 2:19"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Izethekeli zomyeni zingazila kanjani eseselazo na? Zingeke, nxa elokhu eseselazo.</char> <verse eid="MRK 2:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 2:20"/><char style="wj">Kodwa sizafika isikhathi lapho umyeni ezasuswa kuzo, zizazila mhlalokho-ke.</char><verse eid="MRK 2:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 2:21"/>
    <char style="wj">Kakho othungela isichibi selembu elitsha esigqokweni esidala. Nxa ekwenza lokho, isichibi esitsha sizadonsa esidala, ukudabuka kuqhele ngamandla.</char> <verse eid="MRK 2:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 2:22"/><char style="wj">Njalo kakho othela iwayini elitsha emigodleni yezikhumba emidala. Angakwenza lokho iwayini lizaziqhekeza izikhumba kuthi iwayini kanye lemigodla leyo yezikhumba kuhle konakale. Hatshi, uthela iwayini elitsha emigodleni yezikhumba emitsha.”</char><verse eid="MRK 2:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">INkosi YeSabatha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 2:23"/>Ngelinye iSabatha uJesu wayedabula emasimini amabele, kwathi abafundi bakhe belokhu behamba bakha izikhwebu zamabele. <verse eid="MRK 2:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 2:24"/>AbaFarisi bathi kuye, “Khangela, bakwenzelani ukwephula umthetho ngokwenza lokhu ngeSabatha na?”<verse eid="MRK 2:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 2:25"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kalifundanga yini okwenziwa nguDavida labakhula bakhe lapho basebelambile sebeswele?</char> <verse eid="MRK 2:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 2:26"/><char style="wj">Ngezinsuku zika-Abhiyatha umphristi omkhulu wangena endlini kaNkulunkulu wadla isinkwa esingcwelisiweyo, esivunyelwe ukudliwa ngabaphristi kuphela. Futhi wasabela abakhula bakhe.”</char><verse eid="MRK 2:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 2:27"/>Wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“ISabatha lenzelwa abantu, hatshi ukuthi umuntu wenzelwa iSabatha.</char> <verse eid="MRK 2:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 2:28"/><char style="wj">Yikho iNdodana yoMuntu iyiNkosi njalo yeSabatha.”</char><verse eid="MRK 2:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="MRK 3"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usilisa NgeSabatha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 3:1"/>Ngesinye isikhathi uJesu wangena esinagogweni, kukhona lapho indoda elesandla esitshwabheneyo. <verse eid="MRK 3:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 3:2"/>Abanye babo babedinga izaba lokubeka uJesu icala, yikho bamlinda ukubona ingabe wayezasilisa ngeSabatha. <verse eid="MRK 3:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 3:3"/>UJesu wathi endodeni yesandla esitshwabheneyo, <char style="wj">“Sukuma ume phambi kwabo bonke.”</char><verse eid="MRK 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 3:4"/>UJesu wasebabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kuyini okusemthethweni ngeSabatha; ukwenza okuhle loba ukwenza okubi, ukusindisa impilo kumbe ukubulala?”</char> Kodwa bathula zwi.<verse eid="MRK 3:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 3:5"/>Wabakhangela ngolaka, ehlutshwa yibuqholo bezinhliziyo zabo, wasesithi kuleyondoda, <char style="wj">“Yelula isandla sakho.”</char> Yaselula, isandla sesilunge saphelela. <verse eid="MRK 3:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 3:6"/>AbaFarisi basebephuma bayacebisana lamaHerodiya ukuthi bangambulala njani uJesu.<verse eid="MRK 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amaxuku Alandela UJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 3:7"/>UJesu wasuka labafundi bakhe baya ngasechibini, ixuku elikhulu labalandela lisuka eGalile. <verse eid="MRK 3:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 3:8"/>Bathi ngokuzwa konke ayekwenza abantu abanengi beza kuye besuka eJudiya, eJerusalema, e-Idumiya lemimangweni engaphetsheya kweJodani lezindaweni zeThire leSidoni. <verse eid="MRK 3:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 3:9"/>Ngenxa yobunengi babantu watshela abafundi bakhe ukuba bamlungisele isikepe esincane ukuze angaminyezelwa ngabantu. <verse eid="MRK 3:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 3:10"/>Phela wayesesilise abanengi, yikho labo ababelezifo babeminyezela befuna ukumthinta. <verse eid="MRK 3:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 3:11"/>Kwakusithi imimoya emibi ingambona iguqe phambi kwakhe imemeze ithi, “UyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu.” <verse eid="MRK 3:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 3:12"/>Kodwa wayiqonqosela ukuthi ingaze yakhuluma ukuthi ungubani.<verse eid="MRK 3:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukukhethwa Kwabapostoli Abalitshumi Lambili</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 3:13"/>UJesu wakhwela waya ewatheni lwentaba wabiza labo ayebafuna, beza kuye. <verse eid="MRK 3:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 3:14"/>Wakhetha abalitshumi lambili ukuthi babelaye ukuze abathume ukuyatshumayela <verse eid="MRK 3:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 3:15"/>lokuthi babelamandla okuxotsha amadimoni.<verse eid="MRK 3:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 3:16"/>Yilaba abalitshumi lambili abakhethayo:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="MRK 3:16"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="MRK 3:16">uSimoni (ametha ibizo wathi nguPhethro),<verse eid="MRK 3:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 3:17"/>uJakhobe indodana kaZebhediya lomfowabo uJohane (laba wabetha ibizo wathi bango Bhowanegesi, okutsho ukuthi Amadodana Omdumo),<verse eid="MRK 3:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 3:18"/>u-Andreya,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MRK 3:18">uFiliphu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MRK 3:18">uBhatholomewu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MRK 3:18">uMatewu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MRK 3:18">uThomasi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MRK 3:18">uJakhobe indodana ka-Alifewu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MRK 3:18">uThediyasi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MRK 3:18">uSimoni umZilothi<verse eid="MRK 3:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 3:19"/>loJudasi Iskariyothi onguye owamnikelayo.<verse eid="MRK 3:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu LoBhelizebhubhi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 3:20"/>UJesu wangena kwenye indlu kwaphinda njalo kwabuthana kuye ixuku, yena labafundi bakhe baze behluleka ukudla. <verse eid="MRK 3:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 3:21"/>Kwathi abendlu yangakwabo bekuzwa lokho bamlanda ukuyambuyisa ngoba bathi, “usephambene.”<verse eid="MRK 3:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 3:22"/>Kwathi abafundi bomthetho abehla bevela eJerusalema bathi, “Ungenwe nguBhelizebhubhi! Ukhupha amadimoni ngenkosi yamadimoni.”<verse eid="MRK 3:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 3:23"/>Ngakho uJesu wasebabiza wakhuluma labo ngemizekeliso wathi, <char style="wj">“Kambe uSathane angamkhupha kanjani uSathane?</char> <verse eid="MRK 3:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 3:24"/><char style="wj">Nxa umbuso udabuke phakathi, uvukelana, lowombuso ngeke ume.</char> <verse eid="MRK 3:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 3:25"/><char style="wj">Nxa indlu ingabambananga, ivukelana, leyondlu ngeke ime.</char> <verse eid="MRK 3:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 3:26"/><char style="wj">Njalo nxa uSathane eziphikisa, edabuke phakathi, ngeke ame; useyatshabalala.</char> <verse eid="MRK 3:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 3:27"/><char style="wj">Ngempela, akakho ongangena endlini yesiqhwaga, abuthe impahla zaso ngaphandle kokuthi aqale asibophe lesosiqhwaga, andubana aphange indlu yaso.</char> <verse eid="MRK 3:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 3:28"/><char style="wj">Ngeqiniso ngithi kini, abantu bazakuthethelelwa zonke izono lokuhlambaza kwabo,</char> <verse eid="MRK 3:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 3:29"/><char style="wj">kodwa loba ngubani othuka uMoya oNgcwele akayikuthethelelwa; ulecala lesono saphakade.”</char><verse eid="MRK 3:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 3:30"/>Wakutsho lokhu ngoba babesithi, “Ulomoya omubi.”<verse eid="MRK 3:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Unina KaJesu Labafowabo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 3:31"/>Kwasekufika unina kaJesu labafowabo. Bema phandle bathuma omunye umuntu ukuyambiza. <verse eid="MRK 3:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 3:32"/>Abantu abanengi babehlezi bemhanqile, basebemtshela bathi, “Unyoko labafowenu baphandle bayakudinga.”<verse eid="MRK 3:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 3:33"/>Wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngobani abangumama labafowethu na?”</char><verse eid="MRK 3:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 3:34"/>Wasekhangela labo ababehlezi laye bemhanqile wathi, <char style="wj">“Nampa abangumama labangabafowethu!</char> <verse eid="MRK 3:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 3:35"/><char style="wj">Loba ngubani owenza intando kaNkulunkulu ungumfowethu, ungudadewethu njalo ngumama.”</char><verse eid="MRK 3:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="MRK 4"/>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Womhlanyeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 4:1"/>UJesu waphinda njalo wafundisa okhunjini lwesiziba. Ixuku labantu elaqoqana labuthana kuye laba likhulu kakhulu waze wangena esikepeni wahlala kuso siphakathi kwamanzi, kodwa abantu bonke bona bethe gwaqa okhunjini ekucineni kwamanzi. <verse eid="MRK 4:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 4:2"/>Wabafundisa izinto ezinengi ngemizekeliso, ekufundiseni kwakhe wathi: <verse eid="MRK 4:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 4:3"/><char style="wj">“Lalelani! Umlimi waphuma wayahlanyela inhlanyelo yakhe.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 4:4"/><char style="wj">Kwathi eyihaza inhlanyelo, enye yawela endleleni, kwafika izinyoni zayidobha.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 4:5"/><char style="wj">Eyinye yawela okhetheni lapho okwakungela mhlabathi owaneleyo. Yamila masinyane ngoba umhlabathi wawungatshoni.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 4:6"/><char style="wj">Kodwa kwathi ilanga seliphumile, yahanguka yabuna ngoba yayingelampande.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 4:7"/><char style="wj">Enye inhlanyelo yawela emeveni asuka akhula aminya leyonhlanyelo yaze yehluleka ukuthela izikhwebu.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 4:8"/><char style="wj">Eyinye inhlanyelo yawela emhlabathini omuhle. Yamila, yakhula, yathela amabele yanda ngamatshumi amathathu, ayisithupha ngitsho langekhulu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 4:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 4:9"/>UJesu wasesithi, <char style="wj">“Lowo olendlebe zokuzwa kezwe.”</char><verse eid="MRK 4:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 4:10"/>Kwathi eseyedwa, abalitshumi lambili labanye ababeseduze laye bambuza mayelana lemizekeliso leyo. <verse eid="MRK 4:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 4:11"/>Wabatshela wathi, <char style="wj">“Imfihlakalo yombuso kaNkulunkulu seliyambulelwe. Kodwa kulabo abangaphandle konke kukhulunywa ngemizekeliso</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 4:12"/><char style="wj">ukuze,</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 4:12">
    <char style="wj">‘bazahlala bebona kokuphela</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 4:12">
    <char style="wj">kodwa bengabonisisi, njalo bahlale besizwa</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 4:12">
    <char style="wj">kodwa bengaqedisisi funa baphenduke bathethelelwe!’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">4.12 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 6.9-10</char>
    </note>
    <char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="MRK 4:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 4:13"/>UJesu wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Kaliwuzwisisi na umzekeliso lo? Pho lizawuzwa kanjani loba yiwuphi umzekeliso?</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 4:14"/><char style="wj">Umlimi uhlanyela ilizwi.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 4:15"/><char style="wj">Abanye abantu bafana lenhlanyelo esendleleni okuhlanyelwe khona ilizwi. Bonela ukuthi balizwe uSathane uyafika alithathe ilizwi elihlanyelwe kubo.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 4:16"/><char style="wj">Abanye, njengenhlanyelo eyahlanyelwa okhetheni bayalizwa ilizwi bahle balamukele ngentokozo.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 4:17"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngenxa yokuthi kabalampande bema okwesikhatshana kuphela. Kungafika uhlupho loba ukuhlukuluzwa komhlaba baphanga bawe.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 4:18"/><char style="wj">Kunjalo abanye, njengenhlanyelo ehlanyelwe emeveni, bayalizwa ilizwi;</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 4:19"/><char style="wj">kodwa ukuphisekela izinto zalumhlaba, inkohliso yenotho kanye lezinkanuko zezinye izinto konke kuyeza kuliminyanise ilizwi, kulenze lingatheli.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 4:20"/><char style="wj">Abanye, njengenhlanyelo ehlanyelwe emhlabathini omuhle, bayalizwa ilizwi, balamukele, bathele izithelo, bedlule okwakuhlanyelwe ngamatshumi amathathu, ayisithupha loba ngekhulu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 4:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isibane Oluthini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 4:21"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Uyalumathisa isibane usifake ngaphansi kwesitsha kumbe ngaphansi kombheda na? Kawusibeki oluthini lwaso yini?</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 4:22"/><char style="wj">Ngoba loba yini efihliweyo kumele yambulwe, lalokho okuthukuziweyo kumele kuvezwe obala.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 4:23"/><char style="wj">Nxa ekhona olendlebe zokuzwa kezwe.”</char><verse eid="MRK 4:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 4:24"/>Waqhubeka wathi, <char style="wj">“Kuqapheliseni lokho elikuzwayo. Ngaleso isilinganiso elisisebenzisayo lizalinganiselwa ngaso kumbe kuze kwedlulise.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 4:25"/><char style="wj">Lowo olakho uzakwengezelelwa; lowo ongelakho lalokho alakho uzakwemukwa.”</char><verse eid="MRK 4:25"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wenhlamvu Ekhulayo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 4:26"/>Waphinda wathi, <char style="wj">“Umbuso wezulu ufana lalokhu. Indoda ihaza inhlanyelo emhlabathini.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 4:27"/><char style="wj">Ebusuku lemini ingabe ilele loba ikhangele inhlanyelo iyamila ikhule loba yona ingakwazi ukuthi kwenzeka njani.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 4:28"/><char style="wj">Umhlabathi uyiwo wodwa uthela amabele, kuqala ikhaba kuze isikhwebu besekusiza inhlamvu ezikhwetshini.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 4:29"/><char style="wj">Kuthi amabele angavuthwa iwavune ngesikela ngoba ukuvuna sekufikile.”</char><verse eid="MRK 4:29"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wentanga Yemastadi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 4:30"/>Waphinde wathi, <char style="wj">“Sizakuthi umbuso kaNkulunkulu unjengani, kumbe sizasebenzisa umzekeliso bani ukuwuchaza?</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 4:31"/><char style="wj">Unjengentanga yemastadi encinyane kulazo zonke intanga ezihlanyelwa emhlabathini.</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 4:32"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa ihlanyeliwe iyakhula ibe yisihlahla esikhulu kulazo zonke esivandeni, sibe lengatsha ezinkulu ezihlalwa emthunzini waso yizinyoni zezulu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 4:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 4:33"/>UJesu walikhuluma ilizwi kubo ngemizekeliso eminengi enjalo ukuze bazwisise. <verse eid="MRK 4:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 4:34"/>Kazange atsho ulutho kubo engasebenzisanga umzekeliso. Kodwa nxa wayeyedwa labafundi bakhe wachaza konke.<verse eid="MRK 4:34"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uthulisa Isiphepho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 4:35"/>Ngalelolanga sekuntambama wathi kubafundi bakhe, <char style="wj">“Kasihambeni sichaphele ngaphetsheya.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 4:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 4:36"/>Batshiya ixuku, bahamba laye esikepeni enjalo. Zazikhona njalo ezinye izikepe zihamba laye. <verse eid="MRK 4:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 4:37"/>Kwaqubuka isiphepho esesabekayo, amagagasi atshaya esikepeni kwaze kwangathi sesitshona. <verse eid="MRK 4:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 4:38"/>UJesu wayengemuva ezilalele emendlalweni obuthakathaka. Abafundi bamvusa bathi, “Awu, mfundisi kawunanzi yini nxa sigalula?”<verse eid="MRK 4:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 4:39"/>Waphakama wawukhuza umoya wathi emagagasini, “Thulani lithi cwaka!” Ngakho umoya wadeda, kwasekuthula cwaka.<verse eid="MRK 4:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 4:40"/>Wathi kubafundi bakhe, <char style="wj">“Kungani lisesaba kangaka? Lilokhu lingakholwa na?”</char><verse eid="MRK 4:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 4:41"/>Babethuthumela babuzana bathi, “Ungubani lo na? Kambe aze alalelwe ngumoya lamagagasi!”<verse eid="MRK 4:41"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="MRK 5"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukusiliswa Kwendoda Eyayilamadimoni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 5:1"/>Bawela ichibi bafika emangweni wamaGerazini. <verse eid="MRK 5:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 5:2"/>Kwathi uJesu ephuma esikepeni, kwaqhamuka indoda elomoya omubi ivela emathuneni yamhlangabeza. <verse eid="MRK 5:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 5:3"/>Indoda le yayihlala emathuneni, kungaselamuntu ongayibopha loba langeketane. <verse eid="MRK 5:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 5:4"/>Ngoba yayihlezi ibotshiwe izandla lenyawo, kodwa iqamule amaketane lezinsimbi ezinyaweni zayo. Kwakungekho muntu owayelamandla okuyinqoba. <verse eid="MRK 5:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 5:5"/>Ubusuku lemini yayihlaba umkhosi isemathuneni lasezintabeni, izisike ngamatshe.<verse eid="MRK 5:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 5:6"/>Yathi ibona uJesu esesebucwala, yagijima yafika yazilahla phansi ngamadolo phambi kwakhe. <verse eid="MRK 5:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 5:7"/>Yaklabalala ngelizwi elikhulu yathi, “Ufunani ngami, Jesu, Ndodana kaNkulunkulu oPhezukonke? Ngegama likaNkulunkulu ungangihlukuluzi!” <verse eid="MRK 5:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 5:8"/>Ngoba uJesu wayesethe kuyo, <char style="wj">“Phuma kuyo indoda le, wena moya omubi!”</char><verse eid="MRK 5:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 5:9"/>UJesu waseyibuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Ungubani ibizo lakho?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 5:9">Yaphendula yathi, “Ibizo lami nguLigiyoni, ngoba sibanengi.” <verse eid="MRK 5:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 5:10"/>Yamncenga uJesu futhifuthi ukuthi angabaxotshi kulowomango.<verse eid="MRK 5:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 5:11"/>Umhlambi omkhulu wengulube wawusidla ewatheni lwentaba eduzane. <verse eid="MRK 5:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 5:12"/>Amadimoni amncenga uJesu athi, “Sithumele ezingulubeni; sivumele singene kuzo.” <verse eid="MRK 5:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 5:13"/>Wawavumela, omoya ababi baphuma bayangena ezingulubeni. Umhlambi wazo, owawungaba zinkulungwane ezimbili, wagijima usehlela eliweni lodonga wangena echibini wagalula.<verse eid="MRK 5:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 5:14"/>Labo ababezelusile babaleka bayabika lokho edolobheni kanye lasemaphandleni, yikho abantu baqubuka bayabona lokho okwakwenzakele. <verse eid="MRK 5:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 5:15"/>Bathi befika kuJesu bayibona indoda eyayikade ilamadimoni ngobunengi bawo, ihlezi khonapho, igqokile njalo ingqondo isibuyile, besaba kakhulu. <verse eid="MRK 5:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 5:16"/>Labo ababekubonile kusenzakala batshela abantu okwenzakalayo endodeni eyayilamadimoni, balandisa njalo langezingulube. <verse eid="MRK 5:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 5:17"/>Abantu basebemncenga uJesu ukuthi asuke emangweni wakibo.<verse eid="MRK 5:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 5:18"/>Kwathi uJesu esengena esikepeni indoda leyo eyayikade ilamadimoni yamncenga ukuthi ahambe layo. <verse eid="MRK 5:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 5:19"/>UJesu kayivumelanga, kodwa wathi kuyo, <char style="wj">“Hamba ekhaya kwabakini ubatshele ukuba iNkosi ikwenzele okunganani, lokuthi ibe lesihawu kuwe.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 5:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 5:20"/>Ngakho indoda yasihamba yabatshela eDekhapholisi konke uJesu ayeyenzele khona. Bonke abantu bamangala.<verse eid="MRK 5:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Intombazana Efileyo Lomfazi Ogulayo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 5:21"/>Kwathi lapho uJesu esewele njalo ngesikepe waya ngakuleliyana iphetsheya lechibi, kwabuthana kuye ixuku elikhulu ekhonapho eceleni kwechibi. <verse eid="MRK 5:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 5:22"/>Kwasekufika omunye wabaphathi besinagogu okwakuthiwa nguJayirosi, wathi ebona uJesu wazilahla ezinyaweni zakhe. <verse eid="MRK 5:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 5:23"/>Wamncenga kakhulu wathi, “Indodakazi yami encinyane iyafa. Ngicela ubuye uzobeka izandla zakho phezu kwayo ukuze isile njalo iphile.” <verse eid="MRK 5:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 5:24"/>UJesu wahamba laye.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 5:24">Ixuku elikhulu lamlandela laminyezela. <verse eid="MRK 5:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 5:25"/>Kwakulowesifazane khonapho owayephethwe yikopha sekumhluphe iminyaka elitshumi lambili. <verse eid="MRK 5:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 5:26"/>Wayesehlupheke kakhulu loba wayeselatshwa ngabelaphi, njalo esechithe konke ayelakho, kodwa ekubeni abe ngcono kwakusiya phambili. <verse eid="MRK 5:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 5:27"/>Wathi esezwile ngoJesu, weza ngemva kwakhe phakathi kwexuku labantu wabamba isembatho sakhe, <verse eid="MRK 5:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 5:28"/>ngoba wacabanga wathi, “Nxa ngingathinta izigqoko zakhe kodwa nje, ngizasila.” <verse eid="MRK 5:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 5:29"/>Masinyane nje ukopha kwakhe kwaphela njalo wezwa emzimbeni wakhe ukuthi wayesekhululekile ekuhluphekeni kwakhe.<verse eid="MRK 5:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 5:30"/>Khonokho uJesu wananzelela ukuthi amandla ayephumile kuye. Waphendukela exukwini labantu wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngubani othinte izigqoko zami?”</char><verse eid="MRK 5:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 5:31"/>Abafundi bakhe bamphendula bathi, “Lawe uyababona abantu beminyezelana kuwe, kodwa uyabuza uthi, ‘Ngubani ongithintileyo?’ ”<verse eid="MRK 5:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 5:32"/>Kodwa uJesu wala elokhu ethalaza ukuze abone ukuthi ngubani okwenzileyo lokho. <verse eid="MRK 5:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 5:33"/>Ngakho owesifazane owayekwazi okwasekwenzakele kuye weza wazilahla ezinyaweni zakhe eqhaqhazela ngokwesaba wahle wafakaza iqiniso. <verse eid="MRK 5:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 5:34"/>Wathi kowesifazane, <char style="wj">“Ndodakazi, ukholo lwakho lukusilisile. Hamba ngokuthula ukhululeke ekuhluphekeni kwakho.”</char><verse eid="MRK 5:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 5:35"/>UJesu elokhu esakhuluma kweza amanye amadoda ephuma endlini kaJayirasi, umphathi wesinagogu. Athi, “Indodakazi yakho isifile. Kambe usamhluphelani umfundisi na?”<verse eid="MRK 5:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 5:36"/>Akaze akunaka lokho ababekutsho uJesu, wasetshela induna yesinagogu wathi, <char style="wj">“Ungesabi, kholwa nje kuphela.”</char><verse eid="MRK 5:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 5:37"/>Kavumelanga muntu ukuba amlandele ngaphandle kukaPhethro, loJakhobe loJohane umfowabo kaJakhobe. <verse eid="MRK 5:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 5:38"/>Bathi befika emzini wenduna yesinagogu uJesu wabona isiphithiphithi abantu bekhala benqongoloza. <verse eid="MRK 5:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 5:39"/>Wangena wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngesani isiphithiphithi sonke lesi lomkhosi wonke lo? Umntwana kafanga, kodwa ulele.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 5:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 5:40"/>Kodwa bamhleka usulu.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 5:40">Esebakhuphele phandle bonke wathatha uyise womntwana lonina kanye labafundi ayelabo wangena lapho umntwana ayekhona. <verse eid="MRK 5:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 5:41"/>Wambamba ngesandla wathi kuye, <char style="tl"><char style="wj">“Thalitha khumi!”</char></char> (okutsho ukuthi, <char style="wj">“Ntombazana, ngithi kuwe, sukuma!”</char>) <verse eid="MRK 5:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 5:42"/>Masinyane intombazana yasukuma yahambahamba (wayemdala okweminyaka elitshumi lambili). Lokhu kwabamangalisa baphela amandla. <verse eid="MRK 5:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="MRK 5:43"/>Wabaqonqosela wathi bangazisi muntu ngalokho, wasesithi kabamuphe ukudla untombazana.<verse eid="MRK 5:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="MRK 6"/>
  <para style="s1">Umphrofethi Ongeladumo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 6:1"/>UJesu wasuka lapho waya edolobheni lakibo, ehamba labafundi bakhe. <verse eid="MRK 6:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 6:2"/>Kwathi ngeSabatha wafundisa esinagogweni, abanengi abamuzwayo bamangala.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 6:2">Babuzana bathi, “Indoda le yazithatha ngaphi izinto zonke lezi? Yinhlakanipho enganani le ayiphiwayo aze akwazi lokwenza imimangaliso! <verse eid="MRK 6:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 6:3"/>Kanti angithi nguye yini umbazi lo? Kayisindodana kaMariya yini le, umnewabo kaJakhobe, loJosefa, loJuda loSimoni? Odadewabo angithi bakhona khonapha?” Lokho kwenza bamsola.<verse eid="MRK 6:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 6:4"/>UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Umphrofethi kalalo udumo kuphela edolobheni lakibo, phakathi kwezihlobo zakhe lendlini yakwabo.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 6:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 6:5"/>Wayengeke enze izimangaliso khona, ngaphandle kokubeka izandla ebantwini abalutshwana abagulayo ukuba abasilise. <verse eid="MRK 6:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 6:6"/>Njalo wamangaliswa yikusilela kwabo ekukholweni.</para>
  <para style="s1" vid="MRK 6:6">UJesu Uthumela Abalitshumi Lambili</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 6:6">UJesu wasenquma efundisa imizi ngemizi. <verse eid="MRK 6:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 6:7"/>Wabiza abalitshumi lambili beza kuye, wabathumela ngababili wabapha amandla phezu kwemimoya emibi.<verse eid="MRK 6:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 6:8"/>Imilayo yakhe yayiyile: <char style="wj">“Lingathwali lutho kuloluhambo ngaphandle kwentonga, lingathwali isinkwa, isikhwama loba yimali emabhantini enu.</char> <verse eid="MRK 6:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 6:9"/><char style="wj">Ligqoke amanyathela kodwa lingathwali esinye isigqoko.</char> <verse eid="MRK 6:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 6:10"/><char style="wj">Lapho lingena endlini ethile, hlalani khona lize lisuke kulelodolobho.</char> <verse eid="MRK 6:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 6:11"/><char style="wj">Nxa indawo ethile ingalamukeli loba ingalilaleli, dlulani kuleyondawo lithintithe uthuli ezinyaweni zenu kube yibufakazi bokubalahla.”</char><verse eid="MRK 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 6:12"/>Basuka bahamba betshumayela ukuthi abantu kabaphenduke. <verse eid="MRK 6:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 6:13"/>Bakhupha amadimoni amanengi njalo bagcoba abantu abanengi abagulayo ngamafutha babasilisa.<verse eid="MRK 6:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJohane Umbhaphathizi Uqunywa Ikhanda</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 6:14"/>Inkosi uHerodi yezwa ngalokhu, ngoba ibizo likaJesu laselisaziwa kakhulu. Abanye babesithi, “UJohane uMbhaphathizi uvukile kwabafileyo, yikho amandla amangalisayo esebenza kuye.”<verse eid="MRK 6:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 6:15"/>Abanye bathi, “Ungu-Elija.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 6:15">Kwabuye njalo abanye bathi, “Ungumphrofethi, njengomunye wabaphrofethi basendulo.”<verse eid="MRK 6:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 6:16"/>Kodwa kwathi uHerodi ekuzwa lokhu wathi, “UJohane, indoda engayiquma ikhanda usevukile kwabafileyo!”<verse eid="MRK 6:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 6:17"/>Ngoba uHerodi yena ngokwakhe wayekhuphe ilizwi lokuthi uJohane abanjwe, wathi kabotshwe aphoselwe entolongweni. Wakwenza lokho ngenxa kaHerodiyasi, umfazi womfowabo uFiliphu ayesemthethe. <verse eid="MRK 6:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 6:18"/>Ngoba uJohane wayelokhu esithi kuHerodi, “Kawuvunyelwa ukuthi uthathele umfowenu umfazi.” <verse eid="MRK 6:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 6:19"/>Ngakho uHerodiyasi wahlala elesikhwili loJohane efuna ukumbulala. Kodwa waswela indlela yokumbulala, <verse eid="MRK 6:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 6:20"/>ngoba uHerodi wayemesaba uJohane emvikela, ngokumazi ukuthi wayeyindoda elungileyo njalo engcwele. Nxa wayemuzwa uJohane, wayedideka kakhulu, kodwa ethanda ukumlalela.<verse eid="MRK 6:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 6:21"/>Ekucineni lafika elingaliyo. Ngelanga lesikhumbuzo sokuzalwa kwakhe uHerodi wenza idili lezikhulu zakhe labalawuli bempi kanye labakhokheli abaziwayo eGalile. <verse eid="MRK 6:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 6:22"/>Kuthe indodakazi kaHerodiyasi isifikile yagida kamnandi yathokozisa uHerodi lezethekeli zakhe edilini.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 6:22">Inkosi yasisithi entombazaneni, “Ngicela loba yini, ngizakupha.” <verse eid="MRK 6:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 6:23"/>Wamthembisa wafunga wathi, “Loba yini oyicelayo ngizakupha kungaze kube yingxenye yombuso wami.”<verse eid="MRK 6:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 6:24"/>Yaphuma intombazana yayakuthi kunina, “Kambe ngiceleni?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 6:24">Waphendula wathi, “Ikhanda likaJohane uMbhaphathizi.”<verse eid="MRK 6:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 6:25"/>Masinyane intombazana yatheleka enkosini isilesicelo leso, yathi: “Ngifuna ukuthi ungiphe khathesi nje ikhanda likaJohane uMbhaphathizi lisemganwini.”<verse eid="MRK 6:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 6:26"/>Inkosi yakhathazeka kakhulu, kodwa ngenxa yezifungo zayo langenxa yezethekeli zayo kayithandanga ukusala isicelo. <verse eid="MRK 6:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 6:27"/>Ngakho yahle yathumela umbulali ukuba alethe ikhanda likaJohane. Yahamba indoda yamquma ikhanda uJohane entolongweni, <verse eid="MRK 6:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 6:28"/>yaliletha ikhanda lisemganwini. Yalethula entombazaneni, yona yalipha unina. <verse eid="MRK 6:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 6:29"/>Bathi bekuzwa lokho abafundi bakaJohane beza bathatha isidumbu bayasingcwaba ethuneni.<verse eid="MRK 6:29"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Upha Izinkulungwane Ezinhlanu Ukudla</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 6:30"/>Abapostoli babuthana kuJesu bambikela konke ababekwenzile labakufundisayo. <verse eid="MRK 6:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 6:31"/>Kwathi ngoba kwakufika abantu abanengi kakhulu abanye besuka baze baswele ithuba lokudla, wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngilandelani lodwa siye endaweni ethuleyo ukuze siphumule.”</char><verse eid="MRK 6:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 6:32"/>Yikho bahamba bebodwa ngesikepe baya endaweni esithekileyo. <verse eid="MRK 6:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 6:33"/>Kodwa abanengi abababonayo besuka babananzelela babaxhuma begijima ngezinyawo bevela kuwo wonke amadolobho babaqalela ukuyafika. <verse eid="MRK 6:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 6:34"/>UJesu uthe esehla esikepeni wabona ixuku labantu elikhulu wabazwela usizi ngoba babenjengezimvu ezingelamelusi. Ngakho wasebafundisa izinto ezinengi.<verse eid="MRK 6:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 6:35"/>Ngalesi isikhathi kwasekusemini kakhulu, ngakho abafundi bakhe beza kuye bathi, “Le yindawo esesikhaleni, njalo sekusemini kakhulu. <verse eid="MRK 6:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 6:36"/>Tshela abantu bahambe ukuze baziyele emadolobheni lasemizini bayezithengela abangakudla.”<verse eid="MRK 6:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 6:37"/>Kodwa waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Bapheni lina ukudla.”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 6:37">Bathi kuye, “Lokho kungathatha umholo wendoda owenyanga eziyisificaminwembili! Uthi sihambe siyochitha imali engako sithenge isinkwa sibaphe badle?”<verse eid="MRK 6:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 6:38"/>Wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Lilezinkwa ezingaki na? Ake liyokhangela.”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 6:38">Sebezibonile bathi, <char style="wj">“Zinhlanu lenhlanzi ezimbili.”</char><verse eid="MRK 6:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 6:39"/>UJesu wasebalaya ukuthi bahlalise bonke abantu phansi etshanini ngamaxuku. <verse eid="MRK 6:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 6:40"/>Yikho bahlala phansi ngamaxuku alikhulu. Abanye ngamatshumi amahlanu. <verse eid="MRK 6:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 6:41"/>Ethatha izinkwa ezinhlanu lenhlanzi ezimbili wakhangela ezulwini, wabonga, wasehlephuna izinkwa. Waseziqhubela abafundi bakhe ukuba bazabele abantu. Waphinda wabehlukanisela inhlanzi zombili. <verse eid="MRK 6:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 6:42"/>Bonke badla basutha, <verse eid="MRK 6:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="MRK 6:43"/>abafundi basebebutha imvuthu zezinkwa lenhlanzi bagcwalisa izitsha ezilitshumi lambili. <verse eid="MRK 6:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MRK 6:44"/>Abadlayo babengamadoda azinkulungwane ezinhlanu.<verse eid="MRK 6:44"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uhamba Phezu Kwamanzi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="MRK 6:45"/>Masinyane uJesu wenza ukuthi abafundi bakhe bangene esikepeni bahambe bamandulele eBhethisayida, yena esavalelisana labantu. <verse eid="MRK 6:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MRK 6:46"/>Esehlukene labo, waya ewatheni lwentaba ukuyakhuleka.<verse eid="MRK 6:46"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="MRK 6:47"/>Kwathi sekuhlwile isikepe sasiphakathi laphakathi kwechibi, yena eyedwa emhlabathini. <verse eid="MRK 6:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="MRK 6:48"/>Wabona abafundi begwedla ngamandla emagagasini ngoba umoya wawuphambana labo. Kwathi ngomlindo wesine ebusuku waya kubo ehamba phezu kwechibi. Wayengathi usesedlula kubo <verse eid="MRK 6:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="MRK 6:49"/>kodwa bathi bembona ehamba phezu kwesiziba bacabanga ukuthi lithonga. Bahlaba umkhosi <verse eid="MRK 6:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="MRK 6:50"/>ngoba bonke bambona besaba.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 6:50">Masinyane wabakhulumisa wathi, <char style="wj">“Manini isibindi! Yimi. Lingesabi.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 6:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="MRK 6:51"/>Wasengena kubo esikepeni umoya wahle wathula. Bamangala kakhulu, <verse eid="MRK 6:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="MRK 6:52"/>ngoba babengazwisisanga ngezinkwa; inhliziyo zabo zazilukhuni.<verse eid="MRK 6:52"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v" sid="MRK 6:53"/>Bathi sebechaphile, bafikela eGenesaretha bamisa khonapho. <verse eid="MRK 6:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="MRK 6:54"/>Bonela ukuphuma esikepeni abantu bahle bamnanzelela uJesu. <verse eid="MRK 6:54"/><verse number="55" style="v" sid="MRK 6:55"/>Bagijima indawana yonke kulowomango bethwala abagulayo ngamacansi bebasa kuzozonke indawo ababemzwela khona. <verse eid="MRK 6:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="MRK 6:56"/>Loba wayengaze aye ngaphi, emizini, emadolobheni loba emaphandleni, babeka abagulayo ezindaweni zokuthengisela. Bamncenga ukuthi abavumele bathinte nje umphetho wesigqoko sakhe, kwathi bonke labo abamthintayo basila.<verse eid="MRK 6:56"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="MRK 7"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuhlanzeka Lokungahlanzeki</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 7:1"/>AbaFarisi labanye abafundisi bomthetho ababesuka eJerusalema babuthana kuJesu <verse eid="MRK 7:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 7:2"/>babona abanye abafundi bakhe besidla ukudla ngezandla ezazingahlanzekanga, okutsho ukuthi zazingagezwanga. <verse eid="MRK 7:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 7:3"/>(AbaFarisi labaJuda bonke kabadli bengagezanga izandla zabo ngokomthetho, belandela isiko labadala. <verse eid="MRK 7:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 7:4"/>Nxa bevela emsikeni kabadli bengaqalanga bageza. Balandela amasiko amanengi, njengokugezisa amankomitsho, indiwo lamagedlela.)<verse eid="MRK 7:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 7:5"/>Ngakho abaFarisi labafundisi bomthetho bambuza uJesu bathi, “Kungani abafundi bakho bengalandeli amasiko abadala kulokudla ukudla kwabo ngezandla ‘ezingahlanzekanga na’?”<verse eid="MRK 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 7:6"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“U-Isaya wayeqinisile aze aphrofithe ngani lina bazenzisi; njengoba kulotshiwe ukuthi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 7:6">
    <char style="wj">‘Lababantu bangidumisa ngezindebe zabo,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 7:6">
    <char style="wj">kodwa inhliziyo zabo zikhatshana lami.</char><verse eid="MRK 7:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 7:7"/>
    <char style="wj">Bangikhonza ngeze;</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 7:7">
    <char style="wj">imfundiso yabo yimithetho kuphela evela ebantwini.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">7.7 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 29.13</char>
    </note><verse eid="MRK 7:7"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 7:8"/>
    <char style="wj">Seliyekele imilayo kaNkulunkulu labambelela emasikweni abantu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 7:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 7:9"/>Wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Lilendledlana yenu yokufuqela eceleni imilayo kaNkulunkulu ukuze lilandele amasiko enu!</char> <verse eid="MRK 7:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 7:10"/><char style="wj">Phela uMosi wathi, ‘Hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 20.12; UDutheronomi 5.16</char></note> <char style="wj">njalo, ‘Lowo othuka uyise loba unina kumele abulawe.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 21.17; ULevi 20.9</char></note> <verse eid="MRK 7:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 7:11"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lina lithi nxa umuntu esithi lokho obekungaba lusizo kuyise kumbe unina liKhobhani (okutsho ukuthi yisipho esabelwe uNkulunkulu),</char> <verse eid="MRK 7:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 7:12"/><char style="wj">beselisithi angamenzeli lutho uyise loba unina.</char> <verse eid="MRK 7:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 7:13"/><char style="wj">Ngaleyondlela lichitha ilizwi likaNkulunkulu ngamasiko enu eliwedlulisela kuzizukulwane zenu. Futhi lenza izinto ezinengi ezinjalo.”</char><verse eid="MRK 7:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 7:14"/>UJesu waphinda wabiza ixuku labantu wathi, <char style="wj">“Lalelani kimi lonke, lizwisise lokhu.</char> <verse eid="MRK 7:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 7:15"/><char style="wj">Kakulalutho olungaphandle komuntu olungamenza ‘angahlanzeki’ ngokungena kuye. Kodwa yilokho okuphuma phakathi komuntu okuyikho okumenza ‘angahlanzeki.’</char> [<verse eid="MRK 7:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 7:16"/><char style="wj">Nxa ekhona olendlebe zokuzwa kezwe.</char>]<char style="wj">”</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.16 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi ayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note><verse eid="MRK 7:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 7:17"/>Esesukile exukwini labantu wangena endlini abafundi bakhe bambuza ngomzekeliso lo. <verse eid="MRK 7:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 7:18"/>Wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kaliqedisisi ngani na? Kalikuboni yini ukuthi kakulalutho olungena emuntwini lusuka ngaphandle olungamenza ‘angahlanzeki’?</char> <verse eid="MRK 7:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 7:19"/><char style="wj">Ngoba kalungeni enhliziyweni yakhe kodwa luya esiswini sakhe luphinde luphume emzimbeni wakhe.”</char> (Ngokutsho lokhu uJesu waphawula ukuthi konke ukudla kuhlanzekile.)<verse eid="MRK 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 7:20"/>Waqhubeka wathi: <char style="wj">“Okuphuma phakathi komuntu yikho okumngcolisayo.</char> <verse eid="MRK 7:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 7:21"/><char style="wj">Ngoba okusuka ngaphakathi, okusuka enhliziyweni, kuphuma imicabango emibi, ukuhlobonga, ubusela, ukubulala, ukufeba,</char> <verse eid="MRK 7:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 7:22"/><char style="wj">ubuhwaba, umona, ubuqili, ukuxhwala, umhawu, ukugcona, ubuqholo lobuthutha.</char> <verse eid="MRK 7:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 7:23"/><char style="wj">Zonke lezi izono ziphuma ngaphakathi zenze umuntu angcole.”</char><verse eid="MRK 7:23"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukholo lomfazi WomSirofenikhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 7:24"/>UJesu wasuka kuleyondawo waya emangweni waseThire. Wangena endlini kodwa kafunanga ukuthi kwaziwe; kodwa wayengeke azifihle ukuthi ukhona. <verse eid="MRK 7:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 7:25"/>Owesifazane owayelendodakazi yakhe encinyane eyayilomoya omubi wonela ukuzwa ngaye weza wayazilahla ezinyaweni zakhe. <verse eid="MRK 7:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 7:26"/>Umfazi lo wayengumGrikhi, owazalelwa eFenikhe yaseSiriya. Wancenga uJesu ukuthi akhuphe idimoni endodakazini yakhe.<verse eid="MRK 7:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 7:27"/>Wamtshela wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Qala wekele abantwana badle basuthe, ngoba kakulunganga ukuthatha isinkwa sabantwana usiphosele izinja.”</char><verse eid="MRK 7:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 7:28"/>Wathi owesifazane, “Yebo, Nkosi, kodwa izinja lazo ezingaphansi kwetafula ziyadla imvuthuluka.”<verse eid="MRK 7:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 7:29"/>UJesu wamtshela wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngenxa yempendulo enhle kangaka usungahamba; idimoni seliphumile endodakazini yakho.”</char><verse eid="MRK 7:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 7:30"/>Owesifazane wabuyela ekhaya wafumana umntanakhe elele embhedeni, idimoni selihambile.<verse eid="MRK 7:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukusiliswa Kwendoda Eyisacuthe, Eyisimungulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 7:31"/>UJesu wasesuka endaweni yeThire wadabula eSidoni waze wayafika oLwandle lwaseGalile wehla waya emangweni waseDekhapholisi. <verse eid="MRK 7:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 7:32"/>Khonale abantu bamlethela indoda eyayiyisacuthe isehluleka lokukhuluma, bamcela ukuthi abeke isandla sakhe phezu kwayo.<verse eid="MRK 7:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 7:33"/>UJesu wayisusela eceleni kwexuku labantu wasefaka iminwe yakhe ezindlebeni zaleyondoda. Wasekhafula wathinta ulimi lwayo indoda. <verse eid="MRK 7:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 7:34"/>Wakhangela ezulwini wakhokha umoya wathi kuyo, <char style="tl"><char style="wj">“Efifatha!”</char></char> (okutsho ukuthi, <char style="wj">“Vuleka!”</char>). <verse eid="MRK 7:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 7:35"/>Ngalokhu indlebe zendoda zavuleka, ulimi lwayo lwatshwaphuluka yahle yaqalisa ukukhuluma kuhle.<verse eid="MRK 7:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 7:36"/>UJesu wabaqonqosela ukuthi bangatsheli muntu. Kodwa wathi ngokwenza njalo baqhubeka ngamandla befakaza ngakho. <verse eid="MRK 7:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 7:37"/>Abantu bamangala baphela amandla. Bathi, “Konke asekwenzile kuhle. Uyenza futhi lezacuthe zizwe, lezimungulu zikhulume.”<verse eid="MRK 7:37"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="MRK 8"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usuthisa Abazinkulungwane Ezine</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 8:1"/>Ngalezonsuku kwaphinde kwabuthana elinye ixuku labantu. Kwathi ngoba bengelalutho lokudla uJesu wabiza abafundi bakhe wathi kubo, <verse eid="MRK 8:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 8:2"/><char style="wj">“Ngilosizi ngalaba abantu; sebebe lami okwensuku ezintathu, kodwa bengadli lutho.</char> <verse eid="MRK 8:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 8:3"/><char style="wj">Ngingababuyisela emakhaya belambile bazayatha endleleni ngoba abanye babo bavela khatshana.”</char><verse eid="MRK 8:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 8:4"/>Abafundi bakhe baphendula bathi, “Kodwa kungaphi endaweni emi yodwa kanje umuntu angathola khona izinkwa ezanele ukubapha?”<verse eid="MRK 8:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 8:5"/>UJesu wababuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Lilezinkwa ezingaki na?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 8:5">Bathi, “Eziyisikhombisa.”<verse eid="MRK 8:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 8:6"/>Wasetshela ixuku labantu ukuthi lihlale phansi. Wathi esezithethe izinkwa eziyisikhombisa njalo esebongile, wazihlephula waziqhubela abafundi bakhe ukuba baqhubele abantu. Lakanye benza khonokho. <verse eid="MRK 8:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 8:7"/>Njalo babelenhlanzi ezincane ezimbalwa, wazikhulekela lazo wathi abafundi bazabele abantu. <verse eid="MRK 8:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 8:8"/>Abantu badla basutha. Ngemva kwalokho abafundi badobha imvuthu kwagcwala izitsha eziyisikhombisa. <verse eid="MRK 8:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 8:9"/>Ababekhona kwakungamadoda azinkulungwane ezine. Esebabuyisele emakhaya, <verse eid="MRK 8:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 8:10"/>wangena esikepeni labafundi bakhe baya emangweni waseDalimanutha.<verse eid="MRK 8:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 8:11"/>AbaFarisi beza baqalisa ukumbuza uJesu. Bamlinga ngokuthi kabatshengise isibonakaliso esivela ezulwini. <verse eid="MRK 8:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 8:12"/>Wakhokha umoya ngamandla wathi, <char style="wj">“Kungani isizukulwane lesi sicela isibonakaliso? Ngiqinisile ngithi kini, kakulasibonakaliso esizakuphiwa lesisizukulwane.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 8:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 8:13"/>Wasesuka kubo wabuyela esikepeni wachaphela ngakwelinye iphetsheya.<verse eid="MRK 8:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Imvubelo YabaFarisi LoHerodi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 8:14"/>Abafundi bakhohlwa ukuza lesinkwa ngaphandle kwesisodwa ababelaso esikepeni. <verse eid="MRK 8:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 8:15"/>UJesu wabaxwayisa wathi, <char style="wj">“Limukani, liqaphele imvubelo yabaFarisi lekaHerodi.”</char><verse eid="MRK 8:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 8:16"/>Bakhulumisana ngalokhu bathi, “Utsho ngoba singelasinkwa.”<verse eid="MRK 8:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 8:17"/>UJesu wakunanzelela ababekukhuluma, wasebabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kungani likhuluma ngokungabi lasinkwa na? Lilokhu lingaboni njalo lingazwisisi na? Inhliziyo zenu sezintunyile na?</char> <verse eid="MRK 8:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 8:18"/><char style="wj">Kungani lithi lilamehlo lehluleke ukubona, lilezindlebe lehluleke ukuzwa? Kalikhumbuli yini?</char> <verse eid="MRK 8:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 8:19"/><char style="wj">Ngize ngihlephunele abazinkulungwane ezinhlanu izinkwa ezinhlanu labutha izitsha ezingaki zemvuthu?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 8:19">Bathi, “Ezilitshumi lambili.”<verse eid="MRK 8:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 8:20"/>
    <char style="wj">“Ngize ngihlephunele abazinkulungwane ezine izinkwa eziyisikhombisa labutha imvuthu kwaba yizitsha ezingaki na?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 8:20">Baphendula bathi, “Eziyisikhombisa.”<verse eid="MRK 8:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 8:21"/>Wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Lilokhu lingezwisisi yini?”</char><verse eid="MRK 8:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukusiliswa Kwesiphofu EBhethisayida</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 8:22"/>Bafika eBhethisayida, abanye abantu baletha indoda eyayiyisiphofu bancenga uJesu ukuba ayibeke izandla. <verse eid="MRK 8:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 8:23"/>Wasithatha isiphofu leso wasibamba ngesandla wasiholela ngaphandle komuzi. Esekhafulele emehlweni aso wasibeka izandla uJesu wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kukhona okubonayo na?”</char><verse eid="MRK 8:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 8:24"/>Sathalaza sathi, “Ngibona abantu; bakhangeleka njengezihlahla ezihambahambayo.”<verse eid="MRK 8:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 8:25"/>UJesu waphinde wabeka izandla zakhe emehlweni ayo indoda leyo. Amehlo ayo avuleka, yabona kuhle, isibona zonke izinto kakuhle. <verse eid="MRK 8:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 8:26"/>UJesu wayibuyisela ekhaya layo wathi, <char style="wj">“Ungayi edolobheni ukuyakhuluma ngale indaba.”</char><verse eid="MRK 8:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ubufakazi BukaPhethro NgoKhristu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 8:27"/>UJesu labafundi bakhe baya emizini eduze leKhesariya Filiphi. Besendleleni wababuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kambe abantu bathi ngingubani?”</char><verse eid="MRK 8:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 8:28"/>Baphendula bathi, “Abanye bathi unguJohane uMbhaphathizi; abanye bathi ungu-Elija; njalo abanye bathi ungomunye wabaphrofethi.”<verse eid="MRK 8:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 8:29"/>Wasebabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kodwa lina-ke? Lithi ngingubani?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 8:29">UPhethro waphendula wathi, “UnguKhristu.”<verse eid="MRK 8:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 8:30"/>UJesu wabaqonqosela ukuthi bangatsheli muntu ngaye.<verse eid="MRK 8:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ukhuluma Ngokufa Kwakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 8:31"/>Waqalisa ukubafundisa ngokuthi iNdodana yoMuntu imele ihlupheke kakhulu, yaliwe ngabadala bebandla, abaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho, njalo lokuthi kumele ibulawe kuthi ngemva kwensuku ezintathu ivuke njalo. <verse eid="MRK 8:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 8:32"/>Wakukhuluma kamhlophe lokho, uPhethro wamdonsela eceleni waqalisa ukumkhuza.<verse eid="MRK 8:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 8:33"/>Kodwa waphenduka wakhangela abafundi bakhe, wasemkhuza uPhethro wathi, <char style="wj">“Suka emuva kwami, Sathane! Kawunakani ngezinto zikaNkulunkulu, kodwa ngezinto zabantu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 8:33"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Indlela Yesiphambano</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 8:34"/>Wasebiza ixuku labantu kanye labafundi bakhe wathi, <char style="wj">“Nxa umuntu efuna ukungilandela, kumele azidele athathe isiphambano sakhe angilandele.</char> <verse eid="MRK 8:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 8:35"/><char style="wj">Ngoba yilowo ofuna ukulondoloza impilo yakhe izamlahlekela, kodwa olahlekelwa yimpilo yakhe ngenxa yami kanye levangeli uzayilondoloza.</char> <verse eid="MRK 8:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 8:36"/><char style="wj">Kumsizani umuntu ukuzuza wonke umhlaba, kodwa alahlekelwe ngumphefumulo wakhe?</char> <verse eid="MRK 8:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 8:37"/><char style="wj">Loba, kuyini umuntu angakunika kube yinhlawulo yomphefumulo wakhe na?</char> <verse eid="MRK 8:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 8:38"/><char style="wj">Nxa umuntu eyangeka ngami kanye lamazwi ami kulesi isizukulwane esifebayo lesonayo, iNdodana yoMuntu izakuyangeka ngaye nxa isifika enkazimulweni kaYise lezingilosi ezingcwele.”</char><verse eid="MRK 8:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="MRK 9"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 9:1"/>Wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi abanye abemiyo lapha kabayikukuzwa ukufa bengakawuboni umbuso kaNkulunkulu ufika ngamandla.”</char><verse eid="MRK 9:1"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuguquka Isimo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 9:2"/>Ngemva kwensuku eziyisithupha uJesu wathatha uPhethro, loJakhobe loJohane wakhwela labo entabeni ephakemeyo lapho ababa bodwa khona. Bekhona lapho waguquka isimo emehlweni abo. <verse eid="MRK 9:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 9:3"/>Izigqoko zakhe zaba mhlophe njengokukhanya, zaba mhlophe okungazake kwenziwe muntu emhlabeni. <verse eid="MRK 9:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 9:4"/>Khonapho kwabonakala u-Elija loMosi bekhuluma loJesu.<verse eid="MRK 9:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 9:5"/>UPhethro wathi kuJesu, “Rabi, kumnandi kithi ukuba lapha. Kasakhe izihonqo ezintathu esakho, esinye esikaMosi lesinye esika-Elija.” <verse eid="MRK 9:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 9:6"/>(Wayengazi ukuthi athini, babesesaba kakhulu.)<verse eid="MRK 9:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 9:7"/>Kwabuya iyezi labagubuzela, ilizwi labuya livela eyezini lisithi, “Lo yiNdodana yami, engiyithandayo. Ilaleleni!”<verse eid="MRK 9:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 9:8"/>Khonokho nje bathi bayakhangela kababe besabona muntu eduze kwabo ngaphandle kukaJesu.<verse eid="MRK 9:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 9:9"/>Bathi sebesehla entabeni uJesu wabanika imilayo yokuthi bangatsheli muntu ngabakubonileyo iNdodana yoMuntu ize iqale ivuke kwabafileyo. <verse eid="MRK 9:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 9:10"/>Indaba le bayigcina ezifubeni zabo, bebuzana ukuthi, “ukuvuka kwabafileyo” kwakusitshoni.<verse eid="MRK 9:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 9:11"/>Bambuza bathi, “Kungani abafundisi bomthetho besithi u-Elija kumele afike kuqala?”<verse eid="MRK 9:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 9:12"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngeqiniso u-Elija uza kuqala abuyisele izinto zonke esimeni sazo. Kungani pho kulotshiwe ukuthi iNdodana yoMuntu imele ihlupheke kakhulu yaliwe?</char> <verse eid="MRK 9:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 9:13"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngiyalitshela, u-Elija usefikile, sebemenze konke ababekufisa kuye njengoba kulotshiwe ngaye.”</char><verse eid="MRK 9:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukusiliswa Komfana Olomoya Omubi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 9:14"/>Bathi befika kwabanye abafundi babona bebuthanelwe ngabantu abanengi kulabafundisi bomthetho bephikisana labo. <verse eid="MRK 9:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 9:15"/>Abantu bonke bonela ukubona uJesu bamangala kakhulu bamgijimela besiyambingelela.<verse eid="MRK 9:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 9:16"/>Wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kuyini eliphikisana labo ngakho na?”</char><verse eid="MRK 9:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 9:17"/>Kwaphendula indoda ethile exukwini yathi, “Mfundisi, ngikulethele indodana yami ilomoya oyenza ibe yisimungulu. <verse eid="MRK 9:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 9:18"/>Uthi ungayibamba uyilahlele phansi. Isuka ibhubhudle amagwebu, igedle amazinyo, yome qha umzimba. Ngibacelile abafundi bakho ukuthi bawukhuphe umoya, kodwa behluleka.”<verse eid="MRK 9:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 9:19"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Oh, lina sizukulwane esingakholwayo, ngizahlala lani kuze kube nini na? Ngilibekezelele kuze kube nini? Mletheni kimi umfana.”</char><verse eid="MRK 9:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 9:20"/>Basebemletha kuye. Umoya wonela ukumbona uJesu wamlahla phansi umfana wazigiqagiqa ekhihliza amagwebu ngomlomo.<verse eid="MRK 9:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 9:21"/>UJesu wabuza uyise womfana wathi, <char style="wj">“Sekulesikhathi esingakanani enje umfana?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 9:21">Wathi, “Kusukela ebuntwaneni. <verse eid="MRK 9:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 9:22"/>Kuhlezi kumphosela emlilweni loba emanzini kufuna ukumbulala. Kodwa nxa kukhona ongakwenza ake usihawukele usisize.”<verse eid="MRK 9:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 9:23"/>UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Uthi ‘engingakwenza?’ Yonke into iyeneliseka kulowo okholwayo.”</char><verse eid="MRK 9:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 9:24"/>Masinyane uyise womfana wamemeza wathi, “Ngiyakholwa; ake ungisize ngehlule ukungakholwa kwami!”<verse eid="MRK 9:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 9:25"/>UJesu esebona ukuthi ixuku laligijimela kuye wawukhuza umoya omubi wathi, <char style="wj">“Wena moya oyisacuthe lesimungulu, ngiyakulaya mina, ngithi phuma kuye ungaphindi ungene kuye futhi.”</char><verse eid="MRK 9:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 9:26"/>Umoya waklabalala, wamgiqa phansi umfana, waphuma emva kokumhlukuluza okukhulu. Umfana wathi daca, waba njengesidumbu, abanengi bathi, “Usefile.” <verse eid="MRK 9:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 9:27"/>Kodwa uJesu wambamba ngesandla wamdonsa wamisa ngezinyawo wema.<verse eid="MRK 9:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 9:28"/>UJesu esesukile wayangena endlini abafundi bakhe bambuza ngasese bathi, “Kungani sehlulekile ukuwuxotsha na?”<verse eid="MRK 9:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 9:29"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Lolu uhlobo luphuma ngomkhuleko kuphela.”</char><verse eid="MRK 9:29"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ukhuluma Okwesibili Ngokufa Kwakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 9:30"/>Basuka kuleyondawo badabula eGalile. UJesu kazange afune ukuthi kube khona owaziyo ukuthi babengaphi, <verse eid="MRK 9:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 9:31"/>ngoba wayefundisa abafundi bakhe. Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“INdodana yoMuntu izanikelwa ezandleni zabantu. Bazayibulala, kuthi ngemva kwensuku ezintathu izavuka.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 9:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 9:32"/>Kodwa kabezwisisanga ukuthi wayesitshoni njalo besaba ukumbuza ngakho.<verse eid="MRK 9:32"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ngubani Omkhulu Kulabo Bonke?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 9:33"/>Bafika eKhaphenawume. Wathi esendlini wababuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Beliphikisana ngani endleleni?”</char> <verse eid="MRK 9:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 9:34"/>Kodwa bathula zwi ngoba endleleni babephikisana ngokuthi ngubani omkhulu kulabanye bonke.<verse eid="MRK 9:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 9:35"/>Wahlala phansi uJesu wabiza abalitshumi lambili wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Nxa ekhona ofuna ukuba ngowokuqala, kabe ngosekucineni, abe yisisebenzi sabo bonke.”</char><verse eid="MRK 9:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 9:36"/>Wathatha umntwana omncinyane wamisa phakathi kwabo. Wamthatha wamanga wathi kubo, <verse eid="MRK 9:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 9:37"/><char style="wj">“Yilowo owamukela oyedwa walababantwana abancinyane ebizweni lami wamukela mina; njalo lowo ongamukelayo kemukeli mina, kodwa wamukela lowo owangithumayo.”</char><verse eid="MRK 9:37"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ongaphikisani Lathi Umi Lathi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 9:38"/>UJohane wathi, “Mfundisi, sibone indoda ikhupha amadimoni ngebizo lakho, sayenqabela ngoba ingayisuye omunye wethu.”<verse eid="MRK 9:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 9:39"/>UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Lingamaleli. Kakho ongenza umangaliso ngebizo lami aphinde masinyane ajike akhulume okubi ngami,</char> <verse eid="MRK 9:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 9:40"/><char style="wj">ngoba lowo ongamelani lathi ukanye lathi.</char> <verse eid="MRK 9:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 9:41"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso, lowo olipha inkezo yamanzi ngebizo lami ngoba lingabakaKhristu ngempela akayikulahlekelwa ngumvuzo wakhe.”</char><verse eid="MRK 9:41"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukwenzisa Isono</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 9:42"/>
    <char style="wj">“Nxa umuntu ekhubekisa oyedwa walaba abancinyane abakholwa kimi ukuba enze isono, bekungaba ngcono kuye ukuthi aphoselwe olwandle ebotshelwe ilitshe elikhulu entanyeni yakhe.</char> <verse eid="MRK 9:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="MRK 9:43"/><char style="wj">Nxa isandla sakho sikwenza wone, siqume. Kungcono kuwe ukuthi ungene ekuphileni ungungini kulokuya esihogweni ulezandla ezimbili, lapho umlilo wakhona ongacitshiyo,</char> [<verse eid="MRK 9:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MRK 9:44"/><char style="wj">lapho</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 9:44">
    <char style="wj">‘impethu yakhona engafiyo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 9:44">
    <char style="wj">lomlilo wakhona ongacitshiyo.’</char>]<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">9.44 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi ayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note><verse eid="MRK 9:44"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="MRK 9:45"/>
    <char style="wj">Njalo nxa unyawo lwakho lukwenzisa isono, luqume. Kungcono kuwe ukuthi ungene ekuphileni uyisilima kulokuthi ulenyawo ezimbili uphoselwe esihogweni,</char> [<verse eid="MRK 9:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MRK 9:46"/><char style="wj">lapho</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 9:46">
    <char style="wj">‘impethu zakhona ezidlayo zingafi</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 9:46">
    <char style="wj">lomlilo ongacitshiyo.’</char>]<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">9.46 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi ayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note><verse eid="MRK 9:46"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="MRK 9:47"/>
    <char style="wj">Njalo nxa ilihlo lakho likwenza wone, likopole liphume. Kungcono kuwe ukungena embusweni kaNkulunkulu ulelihlo elilodwa kulokuba lamehlo amabili kodwa uphoselwe esihogweni,</char> <verse eid="MRK 9:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="MRK 9:48"/><char style="wj">lapho</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 9:48">
    <char style="wj">‘impethu zakhona ezidlayo zingafi,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 9:48">
    <char style="wj">lomlilo ongacitshiyo.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">9.48 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 66.24</char>
    </note><verse eid="MRK 9:48"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="MRK 9:49"/>
    <char style="wj">Umuntu wonke uzakuvuvuzelwa itswayi ngomlilo.</char><verse eid="MRK 9:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="MRK 9:50"/>
    <char style="wj">Itswayi lilungile, kodwa nxa lingalahlekelwa yibumunyu balo, ungalivuselela njani na? Wobani letswayi ngaphakathi kwenu, lihlalisane ngokuthula.”</char><verse eid="MRK 9:50"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="MRK 10"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuchitha Umtshado</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 10:1"/>UJesu wasesuka kuleyondawo waya emangweni waseJudiya langaphetsheya kweJodani. Njalo kweza kuye amaxuku abantu, kwathi njengenjayelo yakhe wabafundisa.<verse eid="MRK 10:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 10:2"/>Abanye abaFarisi beza bamlinga ngokumbuza bathi, “Kusemthethweni yini ukuthi indoda imale umfazi wayo na?”<verse eid="MRK 10:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 10:3"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“UMosi walilaya wathini?”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 10:4"/>Bathi, “UMosi wayivumela indoda ukuthi ibhale incwadi yokuquma umtshado ibisimxotsha.”<verse eid="MRK 10:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 10:5"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kwakungenxa yokuthi zazilukhuni inhliziyo zenu okwenza uMosi walibhalela umthetho lo.</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 10:6"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ekuqaleni kwendalo uNkulunkulu ‘wabenza baba ngowesilisa lowesifazane.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UGenesisi 1.27</char></note> <verse eid="MRK 10:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 10:7"/><char style="wj">‘Ngalesisizatho indoda izatshiya uyise lonina imanyane lomfazi wayo,</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 10:8"/><char style="wj">kuthi labo bobabili babe nyamanye.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UGenesisi 2.24</char></note> <char style="wj">Yikho kabasebabili, sebemunye.</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 10:9"/><char style="wj">Ngakho, lokho uNkulunkulu asekuhlanganisile akungehlukaniswa muntu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 10:10"/>Bathi sebengenile endlini njalo, abafundi bambuza uJesu ngalokhu. <verse eid="MRK 10:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 10:11"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Loba ngubani olahla umfazi wakhe athathe omunye umfazi uyafeba kuye.</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 10:12"/><char style="wj">Laye nxa elahla indoda yakhe endele kwenye, uyafeba.”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abantwana Abancinyane LoJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 10:13"/>Abantu babeletha abantwana abancinyane kuJesu ukuze ababeke izandla, kodwa abafundi babakhuza. <verse eid="MRK 10:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 10:14"/>UJesu wathi ekubona lokho wacaphuka. Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Yekelani abantwana abancane beze kimi, lingabavaleli, ngoba umbuso kaNkulunkulu ungowabanjengalaba.</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 10:15"/><char style="wj">Ngiqinisile ngithi kini, lowo ongayikwemukela umbuso kaNkulunkulu njengomntwana omncane kayikungena kuwo.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 10:16"/>Wasebathatha abantwana ebaphatha, wababeka izandla wababusisa.<verse eid="MRK 10:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ijaha Elalinothile</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 10:17"/>UJesu wathi esesuka ehamba, indoda yagijimela kuye yafika yazilahla ngamadolo phambi kwakhe. Yabuza yathi, “Mfundisi olungileyo, ngingenzani ukuze ngizuze ilifa lokuphila kwaphakade na?”<verse eid="MRK 10:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 10:18"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ungibizelani ngokuthi ngilungile na? Kakho olungileyo ngaphandle kukaNkulunkulu kuphela.</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 10:19"/><char style="wj">Uyayazi imilayo: ‘Ungabulali, ungafebi, ungebi, ungaphi ubufakazi bamanga, ungadlelezeli, hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10.19 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 20.12-16; UDutheronomi 5.16-20</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 10:20"/>Wachaza wathi, “Mfundisi zonke lezi izinto ngiyazigcina kusukela ngisesengumfana.”<verse eid="MRK 10:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 10:21"/>UJesu wamkhangela wamthanda. Wathi, <char style="wj">“Usilela ngento eyodwa. Hamba uyethengisa konke olakho uphe abampofu, lapho-ke inotho yakho izakuba sezulwini. Ubusubuya ungilandele.”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 10:22"/>Isizwa lokhu indoda yathelwa ngamanzi. Yasukuma yahamba isidanile ngoba yayinothile kakhulu.<verse eid="MRK 10:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 10:23"/>UJesu wathalaza wasesithi kubafundi bakhe, <char style="wj">“Koba nzima kakhulu ukuthi isinothi singene embusweni kaNkulunkulu!”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 10:24"/>Abafundi bamangaliswa ngamazwi akhe lawo. Kodwa uJesu waphinda wathi, <char style="wj">“Bantwana, kunzima kanganani ukungena embusweni kaNkulunkulu!</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 10:25"/><char style="wj">Kulula ukuba ikamela lingene embotsheni yenalithi kulokuba umuntu onothileyo angene embusweni kaNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 10:26"/>Abafundi bamangala okwedlulayo, bathi omunye komunye, “Pho ngubani ongasindiswa na?”<verse eid="MRK 10:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 10:27"/>UJesu wabakhangela wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngokwabantu kakwenzeki, kodwa hatshi ngoNkulunkulu; zonke izinto ziyenzakala ngoNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 10:28"/>UPhethro wathi kuye, “Sesitshiye konke ukuba sikulandele!”<verse eid="MRK 10:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 10:29"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso ngithi kakho osetshiye ikhaya kumbe abafowabo, loba odadewabo, kumbe unina loba uyise, loba umntwana kumbe amasimu ngenxa yami levangeli</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 10:30"/><char style="wj">ozakwehluleka ukwamukeliswa okuphindwe ngekhulu kuso lesi isikhathi samanje: amakhaya, abafowabo, odadewabo, onina, abantwana lamasimu, kwengezwe ukuhlukunyezwa, lasesikhathini esizayo, ukuphila kwaphakade.</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 10:31"/><char style="wj">Kodwa abanengi abangabokuqala bazakuba ngabokucina, abokucina babe ngabokuqala.”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:31"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ufanisa Ukufa Kwakhe Njalo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 10:32"/>Babesendleleni besiya eJerusalema, uJesu ekhokhele, abafundi bedidekile, kwathi labo ababelandela babesesaba. Waphinda njalo wathatha abalitshumi lambili wabadonsela eceleni wabatshela lokho okwakuzakwenzakala kuye. <verse eid="MRK 10:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 10:33"/>Wathi, <char style="wj">“Sesisiya eJerusalema, iNdodana yoMuntu izanikelwa kubaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho. Bazayigwebela ukufa bayinikele kwabeZizwe,</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 10:34"/><char style="wj">abazayiyangisa, bayikhafulele, bayitshaye njalo bayibulale. Ngemva kwensuku ezintathu izavuka.”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:34"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isicelo SikaJakhobe LoJohane</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 10:35"/>Kwathi uJakhobe loJohane, amadodana kaZebhediya, beza kuye. Bathi, “Mfundisi, sifuna ukuthi usenzele loba yini esiyicelayo.”<verse eid="MRK 10:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 10:36"/>Wababuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Lifuna ukuthi ngilenzeleni?”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 10:37"/>Baphendula bathi, “Wothi omunye wethu ahlale ngakwesokunene kwakho, kuthi omunye kwesokhohlo ebukhosini bakho.”<verse eid="MRK 10:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 10:38"/>UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Kalikwazi elikucelayo. Lingayinatha na inkezo engiyinathayo kumbe libhaphathizwe ngobhaphathizo engibhaphathizwa ngalo, na?”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 10:39"/>Baphendula bathi, “Singakwenza.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 10:39">UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Lizayinatha inkezo engiyinathayo njalo libhaphathizwe ngobhaphathizo engibhaphathizwa ngalo,</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 10:40"/><char style="wj">kodwa ukuhlala kwesokunene kumbe kwesokhohlo kwami kakusikho kwami ukukuvumela. Izindawo lezi ngezalabo abazilungiselweyo.”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 10:41"/>Kwathi abalitshumi bekuzwa lokhu bazondela uJakhobe loJohane. <verse eid="MRK 10:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 10:42"/>UJesu wababizela ndawonye wathi, <char style="wj">“Liyakwazi ukuthi labo abangababusi kwabeZizwe bababusa kalukhuni, lezinduna zabo ezinkulu zitshengisa amandla phezu kwabo.</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="MRK 10:43"/><char style="wj">Akunjalo kini. Kodwa lowo othanda ukuba mkhulu phakathi kwenu kumele abe yinceku yenu,</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MRK 10:44"/><char style="wj">lalowo ofuna ukuba ngowokuqala kabe yisigqili senu lonke.</char> <verse eid="MRK 10:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="MRK 10:45"/><char style="wj">Ngoba leNdodana yoMuntu kayibuyelanga ukuzokhonzwa, kodwa ukuzokhonza lokunikela impilo yayo njengenhlawulo yabanengi.”</char><verse eid="MRK 10:45"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isiphofu UBhatholomewu Uvulwa Amehlo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="MRK 10:46"/>Basebefika eJerikho. Kwathi uJesu labafundi bakhe kanye lexuku elikhulu sebesuka edolobheni, indoda eyisiphofu, uBhathimewu (kutsho indodana kaThimewu) yayihlezi eceleni kwendlela icela. <verse eid="MRK 10:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="MRK 10:47"/>Yathi isizwa ukuthi kwakunguJesu waseNazaretha yamemeza yathi, “Jesu, Ndodana kaDavida, ake ungihawukele!”<verse eid="MRK 10:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="MRK 10:48"/>Abanengi bayikhuza bathi kayithule, kodwa yaqhubeka yamemeza ngamandla isithi, “Ndodana kaDavida, ake ungihawukele!”<verse eid="MRK 10:48"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="MRK 10:49"/>UJesu wema wathi, <char style="wj">“Mbizeni.”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 10:49">Basebeyibiza indoda eyisiphofu bathi, “Thokoza ndoda! Phakama! Uyakubiza.” <verse eid="MRK 10:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="MRK 10:50"/>Walahla ijazi lakhe phansi wasukuma weza kuJesu.<verse eid="MRK 10:50"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="MRK 10:51"/>UJesu wambuza wathi, “Ufuna ngikwenzeleni na?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 10:51">Indoda eyisiphofu yathi, “Rabi, ngifuna ukuthi ngibone.”<verse eid="MRK 10:51"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="52" style="v" sid="MRK 10:52"/>UJesu wathi, “Hamba-ke, ukukholwa kwakho sekukusilisile.” Masinyane yahle yabona yasilandela uJesu endleleni.<verse eid="MRK 10:52"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="MRK 11"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukungena Ngobukhosi EJerusalema</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 11:1"/>Bathi sebesondele eJerusalema bafika eBhethifage leBhethani eNtabeni yama-Oliva. UJesu wathuma abafundi bakhe ababili <verse eid="MRK 11:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 11:2"/>wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Yanini emzini ophambi kwenu, okuzakuthi nxa lingena kuwo lizabona inkonyane kababhemi engakaze igadwe muntu ibotshelwe khonapho. Ikhululeni liyilethe lapha.</char> <verse eid="MRK 11:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 11:3"/><char style="wj">Nxa kungaba lozalibuza ukuthi, ‘Likwenzeleni lokho na?’ limtshele ukuthi, ‘INkosi iyalifuna, izalibuyisa masinyane.’ ”</char><verse eid="MRK 11:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 11:4"/>Bahamba bathola inkonyane kababhemi phandle maqondana lomnyango ibotshelwe. Bayikhulula, <verse eid="MRK 11:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 11:5"/>abantu ababemi khonapho babuza bathi, “Lenzani, liyikhululelani inkonyane leyo na?” <verse eid="MRK 11:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 11:6"/>Baphendula njengoba uJesu wayebatshelile, abantu basebebayekela bahamba. <verse eid="MRK 11:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 11:7"/>Sebelilethile ithole kuJesu bendlala amajazi abo phezu kwalo uJesu waseligada. <verse eid="MRK 11:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 11:8"/>Abantu abanengi bendlala amajazi abo endleleni, kukanti abanye bendlala ingatsha abaziqamula emasimini. <verse eid="MRK 11:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 11:9"/>Labo ababehamba phambili lalabo ababelandela bamemeza besithi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 11:9">“Hosana!”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11.9 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 118.25-26</char></note></para>
  <para style="b" vid="MRK 11:9"/>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 11:9">“Ubusisiwe lowo obuya ngebizo leNkosi!”<verse eid="MRK 11:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 11:10"/>“Ubusisiwe umbuso ozayo okababa wethu uDavida!”</para>
  <para style="b" vid="MRK 11:10"/>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 11:10">“Hosana ezulwini eliphezulu!”<verse eid="MRK 11:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 11:11"/>UJesu wangena eJerusalema waya ethempelini. Wathalaza wakhangela konke, kodwa kwathi ngoba kwasekuhlwile wehlela eBhethani labalitshumi lambili.<verse eid="MRK 11:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uhlambulula IThempeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 11:12"/>Ngelanga elilandelayo bathi besuka eBhethani uJesu wayeselambile. <verse eid="MRK 11:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 11:13"/>Wabona bucwadlana isihlahla somkhiwa sihlumile amahlamvu, wasondela ukuyabona ingabe sasilezithelo yini. Wafika wabona kungamahlamvu kuphela ngoba kwakungasiso isikhathi sezithelo zomkhiwa. <verse eid="MRK 11:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 11:14"/>Wasesithi esihlahleni, <char style="wj">“Akungabi lamuntu lanini ozaphinda adle izithelo zakho.”</char> Abafundi bakhe bamuzwa esitsho lokho.<verse eid="MRK 11:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 11:15"/>Bathi befika eJerusalema uJesu wangena egumeni lethempeli wafika wabaxotsha labo ababethenga lababethengisa khona. Wagenqula amatafula abantshintshi bezimali lezihlalo zababethengisa amajuba, <verse eid="MRK 11:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 11:16"/>kaze avumela muntu ukungenisa okuthengiswayo ezindlini zethempeli. <verse eid="MRK 11:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 11:17"/>Wathi esabafundisa wathi, <char style="wj">“Kakulotshwanga yini ukuthi: ‘Indlu yami izabizwa ngokuthi yindlu yokukhuleka ezizweni zonke’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11.17 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 56.7</char></note><char style="wj">? Kodwa lina seliyenze ‘ubhalu lwabaphangi.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11.17 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UJeremiya 7.11</char></note> <char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="MRK 11:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 11:18"/>Abaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho bakuzwa lokhu basebeqalisa ukudinga indlela yokumbulala, ngoba babemesaba ngoba ixuku lonke lalimangaliswa yikufundisa kwakhe.<verse eid="MRK 11:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 11:19"/>Kusihlwa baphuma edolobheni.<verse eid="MRK 11:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umkhiwa Obunileyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 11:20"/>Ekuseni babehambahamba basebebona isihlahla somkhiwa esasibunile kusukela empandeni. <verse eid="MRK 11:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 11:21"/>UPhethro wakhumbula wasesithi kuJesu, “Rabi, khangela! Isihlahla somkhiwa owasiqalekisayo sibunile!”<verse eid="MRK 11:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 11:22"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Woba lokholo kuNkulunkulu.</char> <verse eid="MRK 11:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 11:23"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi nxa omunye esithi entabeni le, ‘Suka, ziphosele olwandle,’ engelakuthandabuza enhliziyweni yakhe, kodwa ekholwa ukuthi lokho akutshoyo kuzakwenzakala, kuzakwenziwa kuye.</char> <verse eid="MRK 11:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 11:24"/><char style="wj">Ngakho ngiyalitshela ukuthi loba kuyini elikucelayo ngomkhuleko, kholwani ukuthi selikwamukele, sekuzakuba ngokwenu.</char> <verse eid="MRK 11:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 11:25"/><char style="wj">Njalo nxa lisima likhuleka, nxa lilesikhwili komunye, mthetheleleni, ukuze uYihlo ezulwini alithethelele izono zenu.</char> [<verse eid="MRK 11:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 11:26"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa lingathetheleli, loYihlo osezulwini kazukulithethelela izono zenu.</char>]<char style="wj">”</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11.26 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi ayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note><verse eid="MRK 11:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amandla KaJesu Ayathandabuzisa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 11:27"/>Bafika njalo eJerusalema, kwathi uJesu ezihambela emagumeni ethempeli kweza kuye abaphristi abakhulu, labafundisi bomthetho kanye labadala. <verse eid="MRK 11:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 11:28"/>Bambuza bathi, “Konke lokhu ukwenza ngawaphi amandla na? Ngubani owakupha amandla okwenza lokhu?”<verse eid="MRK 11:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 11:29"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngizalibuza umbuzo owodwa. Lingangiphendula ngizalitshela ukuthi ngizenza ngawaphi amandla lezizinto.</char> <verse eid="MRK 11:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 11:30"/><char style="wj">Ukubhaphathiza kukaJohane, kwakuvela ezulwini loba ebantwini? Ngitshelani!”</char><verse eid="MRK 11:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 11:31"/>Bahlanganisa amakhanda bathi, Singathi, “ ‘Kwakuvela ezulwini,’ uzabuza athi, ‘Kungani lingazange limkholwe?’ <verse eid="MRK 11:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 11:32"/>Kodwa singathi, ‘Kwakuvela ebantwini’ … ” (Besaba abantu ngoba bonke babesithi ngeqiniso uJohane wayengumphrofethi.)<verse eid="MRK 11:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 11:33"/>Ngakho bamphendula uJesu bathi, “Kasikwazi.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 11:33">UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Lami kangisalitsheli ukuthi izinto lezi ngizenza ngawaphi amandla.”</char><verse eid="MRK 11:33"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="MRK 12"/>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wabaqhatshi Besivini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 12:1"/>Wasekhuluma kubo ngemizekeliso wathi, <char style="wj">“Indoda yahlanyela isivini. Yakha umduli yasihonqolozela, yemba igodi lesihluzo yasisakha umphotshongo wesilindo. Yasiqhatshisa isivini kubalimi abathile yona yasuka yathatha uhambo.</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 12:2"/><char style="wj">Ngesikhathi sokuvuna yathuma isisebenzi kubaqhatshi besivini ukuthi siyothatha ingxenye yezithelo zesivuno.</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 12:3"/><char style="wj">Kodwa basidumela basitshaya basixotsha singaphathanga lutho.</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 12:4"/><char style="wj">Yathuma esinye isisebenzi kubo; leyondoda bayitshaya ekhanda bayiphatha kubi.</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 12:5"/><char style="wj">Yaphinde yathuma esinye njalo isisebenzi, leso bahle basigongoda basibulala. Yathuma ezinye ezinengi; ezinye zazo bazitshaya, ezinye bazibulala.</char><verse eid="MRK 12:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 12:6"/>
    <char style="wj">Kwasekusele oyedwa wokuthuma, indodana, ayeyithanda. Wayithuma ekucineni kwabo bonke esithi, ‘Bazayihlonipha indodana yami.’</char><verse eid="MRK 12:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 12:7"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa abaqhatshi besivini batshelana bathi, ‘Lo yindlalifa. Wozani, simbulale, ilifa libe ngelethu.’</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 12:8"/><char style="wj">Ngakho bamthatha bambulala bamphosela ngaphandle kwesivini.</char><verse eid="MRK 12:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 12:9"/>
    <char style="wj">Kambe kuyini azakwenza umnini wesivini na? Uzakuza afike ababulale labo baqhatshi besivini, isivini leso asinike abanye abalimi.</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 12:10"/><char style="wj">Kalibalanga yini umbhalo lo othi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 12:10">
    <char style="wj">‘Ilitshe elalahlwa ngabakhi</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 12:10">
    <char style="wj">seliyilona ilitshe lekhoneni;</char><verse eid="MRK 12:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 12:11"/>
    <char style="wj">iNkosi ikwenzile lokhu,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 12:11">
    <char style="wj">kuyamangalisa emehlweni ethu’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">12.11 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 118.22-23</char>
    </note>
    <char style="wj">?”</char><verse eid="MRK 12:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 12:12"/>Basebedinga iqinga lokumbopha ngoba babesazi ukuthi wayekhulume umzekeliso lowo eqonde bona. Kodwa besaba ixuku labantu; basebemtshiya bahamba.<verse eid="MRK 12:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuthela KuKhesari</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 12:13"/>Muva basebethumela abanye babaFarisi lamaHerodiya kuJesu ukuthi bambambe ngamazwi akhe. <verse eid="MRK 12:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 12:14"/>Beza kuye bathi, “Mfundisi, siyakwazi ukuthi uyindoda eqotho. Kawuguqulwanga ngabantu ngoba kawulandeli ukuthi bangobani; kodwa ufundisa indlela kaNkulunkulu mayelana leqiniso. Kulungile yini ukuthela kuKhesari, kumbe hatshi? <verse eid="MRK 12:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 12:15"/>Sithele yini kumbe hatshi?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 12:15">Kodwa uJesu wayekubona ukuzenzisa kwabo, wathi, <char style="wj">“Lizamelani ukungithiya na? Ake lingiphe idenari ngibone.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 12:16"/>Baluletha uhlamvu lolo, wasebabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngumfanekiso kabani lo? Lombhalo ngokabani?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 12:16">Baphendula bathi, “NgokaKhesari.”<verse eid="MRK 12:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 12:17"/>UJesu wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Phanini uKhesari okukaKhesari loNkulunkulu okungokukaNkulunkulu.”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 12:17">Bamangala kakhulu ngaye.<verse eid="MRK 12:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuthathana Lokuvuka Ekufeni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 12:18"/>Kwasekusithi abaSadusi abathi kakukho ukuvuka kwabafileyo, beza kuye belombuzo. <verse eid="MRK 12:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 12:19"/>Bathi, “Mfundisi, uMosi wasibhalela ukuthi nxa umfowabo wendoda angafa atshiye umfazi, kodwa bengelabantwana, leyondoda kayimthathe umfelokazi izalele umfowabo abantwana. <verse eid="MRK 12:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 12:20"/>Manje-ke, kwakulabafowabo abayisikhombisa. Owokuqala wathatha wasesifa engazalanga. <verse eid="MRK 12:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 12:21"/>Owesibili wamthatha umfelokazi waphinda laye wafa engelamntwana. Kwabanjalo lakowesithathu. <verse eid="MRK 12:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 12:22"/>Iqiniso yikuthi kakho kubo bonke beyisikhombisa owaba labantwana. Ekucineni kwafa yena umfazi. <verse eid="MRK 12:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 12:23"/>Ekuvukeni kwabafileyo uzakuba ngumkabani njengoba bonke boyisikhombisa babemthethe?”<verse eid="MRK 12:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 12:24"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kalilahleki yini ngoba lingayazi imibhalo loba amandla kaNkulunkulu?</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 12:25"/><char style="wj">Nxa abafileyo sebevuka kabayikuthatha loba bende; bazakuba njengezingilosi ezulwini.</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 12:26"/><char style="wj">Mayelana lokuvuka kwabafileyo, kalibalanga yini encwadini kaMosi, emlandweni wesixuku esasibhebha umlilo ukuthi uNkulunkulu wathi kuye, ‘NginguNkulunkulu ka-Abhrahama, uNkulunkulu ka-Isaka loNkulunkulu kaJakhobe’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12.26 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 3.6</char></note><char style="wj">?</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 12:27"/><char style="wj">KasuNkulunkulu wabafileyo, kodwa owabaphilayo. Lilahlekile kakhulu!”</char><verse eid="MRK 12:27"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umlayo Omkhulu Kulayo Yonke</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 12:28"/>Omunye wabafundisi bomthetho wafika wabezwa bephicana ngamazwi. Ngokubona ukuthi uJesu wayebaphe impendulo enhle, wabuza wathi, “Phakathi kwayo yonke imilayo yiwuphi oqakatheke okudlula yonke?”<verse eid="MRK 12:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 12:29"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, “Oqakatheke kakhulu yilo: <char style="wj">‘Zwana, wena Israyeli, iNkosi uNkulunkulu wethu, iNkosi yinye.</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 12:30"/><char style="wj">Thanda iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho ngenhliziyo yakho yonke langomphefumulo wakho wonke langengqondo yakho yonke langamandla akho wonke.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12.30 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 6.4-5</char></note> <verse eid="MRK 12:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 12:31"/><char style="wj">Owesibili yilo: ‘Thanda umakhelwane wakho njengoba uzithanda.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12.31 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ULevi 19.18</char></note> <char style="wj">Kawukho umlayo omkhulu kulale.”</char><verse eid="MRK 12:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 12:32"/>Indoda yaphendula yathi, “Utsho kuhle, mfundisi. Uqondile nxa usithi uNkulunkulu munye, kakho omunye ngaphandle kwakhe. <verse eid="MRK 12:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 12:33"/>Ukumthanda ngenhliziyo yakho yonke, ngokuzwisisa konke kwakho langamandla akho wonke, lokuthanda umakhelwane wakho njengoba uzithanda wena kuqakathekile kulayo yonke iminikelo yokutshiswa lemihlatshelo.”<verse eid="MRK 12:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 12:34"/>UJesu wathi ebona ukuthi uphendule kuhle wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Kawukho khatshana kombuso kaNkulunkulu.”</char> Kusukela kulesosikhathi kakusabanga khona owaba lesibindi sokumbuza eminye imibuzo.<verse eid="MRK 12:34"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UKhristu UyiNdodana Kabani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 12:35"/>Kwathi uJesu efundisa emagumeni ethempeli wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kungani abafundisi bomthetho besithi uKhristu uyindodana kaDavida na?</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 12:36"/><char style="wj">UDavida yena ngokwakhe ekhuluma ngoMoya oNgcwele wathi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 12:36">
    <char style="wj">‘INkosi yathi eNkosini yami:</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 12:36">
    <char style="wj">“Hlala ngakwesokunene sami</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 12:36">
    <char style="wj">ngize ngibeke izitha zakho</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 12:36">
    <char style="wj">ngaphansi kwenyawo zakho.”</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">12.36 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 110.1</char>
    </note>
    <char style="wj">’</char><verse eid="MRK 12:36"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 12:37"/>
    <char style="wj">UDavida yena ngokwakhe umbiza athi ‘Nkosi.’ Pho-ke angaba yindodana yakhe kanjani?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 12:37">Ixuku labantu elikhulu lamlalela ngokuthokoza.<verse eid="MRK 12:37"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukulimukisa NgabaFundisi BoMthetho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 12:38"/>Wathi elokhu efundisa, uJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Libananzelele abafundisi bomthetho. Bathanda ukuhambahamba becece ngezembatho ezinde eziphephezelayo lokube bebingelelwa emisikeni,</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 12:39"/><char style="wj">futhi bathatha izihlalo eziphakemeyo emasinagogweni lezindawo zabahlonitshwa emadilini.</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 12:40"/><char style="wj">Bahuquluza izindlu zabafelokazi njalo bazibonakalisa ngokwenza imikhuleko emide. Abantu abanjalo bazajeziswa kabuhlungu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 12:40"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umnikelo Womfelokazi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 12:41"/>UJesu wahlala phansi malungana lendawo yokunikela wakhangela inengi lifaka imali yalo esitsheni somnikelo ethempelini: Izikhulu ezinengi zazifaka imali ezwayo. <verse eid="MRK 12:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 12:42"/>Kodwa kweza umfelokazi ongumyanga wafaka okuzinhlamvana kwethusi okubili okulingana lengxenyana yendibilitshi.<verse eid="MRK 12:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="MRK 12:43"/>Esebizele kuye abafundi bakhe uJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi umfelokazi lo ongumyanga ufake okunengi esitsheni somnikelo kulabo bonke.</char> <verse eid="MRK 12:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MRK 12:44"/><char style="wj">Bona bonke baphe ngokwenotho yabo, kodwa yena, ebuyangeni bakhe ufake konke abelakho ukuthi kumphilise.”</char><verse eid="MRK 12:44"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="MRK 13"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukubhidlizwa KweThempeli Lezibonakaliso Zokucina Kwesikhathi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 13:1"/>Wathi esuka ethempelini omunye wabafundi wathi kuye, “Khangela, Mfundisi! Amatshe anganani! Bona ubuhle bezindlu!”<verse eid="MRK 13:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 13:2"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Liyazibona yini zonke lezi izindlu ezinkulu kangaka? Kakuyikusala litshe phezu kwelinye; wonke azaphoselwa phansi.”</char><verse eid="MRK 13:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 13:3"/>Kwathi uJesu ehlezi eNtabeni yama-Oliva malungana lethempeli uPhethro, loJakhobe, loJohane lo-Andreya bambuza ngasese bathi, <verse eid="MRK 13:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 13:4"/>“Sitshele, zizakwenzakala nini izinto lezi? Njalo kuzakuba lesibonelo bani ukuthi sezizagcwaliseka?”<verse eid="MRK 13:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 13:5"/>UJesu wathi kubo: <char style="wj">“Qaphelani ukuze lingakhohliswa muntu.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 13:6"/><char style="wj">Banengi abazakuza ngebizo lami, besithi, ‘Nginguye,’ bakhohlise abanengi.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 13:7"/><char style="wj">Nxa lisizwa ngezimpi lamahungahunga ngezimpi, lingaze lethuka. Lezozinto kumele zenzakale, kodwa ukucina kulokhu kuseza.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 13:8"/><char style="wj">Isizwe sizavukela isizwe, lombuso uvukele umbuso. Kuzakuba lokuzamazama komhlaba ezindaweni ezinengi, lezindlala. Lezi ziyikuqala kokuhelelwa.</char><verse eid="MRK 13:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 13:9"/>
    <char style="wj">Libohlala liqaphele. Bazalimangalela ezinkundleni zamacala njalo balibhaxabule emasinagogweni abo. Ngenxa yami lizamiswa phambi kwababusi lamakhosi libe ngofakazi kubo.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 13:10"/><char style="wj">Njalo ivangeli kufanele liqale litshunyayelwe ezizweni zonke.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 13:11"/><char style="wj">Lapho libotshwa njalo lilethwa emthethwandaba lingaze lazihlupha ngokuthi lizakuthini phambi kwabo. Khulumani ingqe yini eliyiphiwa ngalesosikhathi, ngoba kakusini elikhulumayo, kodwa nguMoya oNgcwele.</char><verse eid="MRK 13:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 13:12"/>
    <char style="wj">Umfowabo uzanikela umfowabo ukuthi abulawe, loyise anikele umntanakhe. Abantwana bazahlamukela abazali babo bababulalise.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 13:13"/><char style="wj">Bonke abantu bazalizonda ngenxa yami, kodwa lowo oma aqine kuze kube sekupheleni uzasindiswa.</char><verse eid="MRK 13:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 13:14"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa nxa libona ‘amanyala aletha incithakalo’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">13.14 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">UDanyeli 9.27; 11.31; 12.11</char>
    </note> <char style="wj">kumi lapho okungesikwakhona, ofundayo kezwisise, lapho-ke akuthi labo abaseJudiya babalekele ezintabeni.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 13:15"/><char style="wj">Akungabikhona osephahleni lwendlu yakhe ozakwehla loba angene endlini ukuthatha ulutho.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 13:16"/><char style="wj">Akungabi loyedwa osensimini ozabuyela emuva ukuyathatha ijazi lakhe.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 13:17"/><char style="wj">Yeka ubulukhuni obuzakuba khona ngalezonsuku kwabesifazane abakhulelweyo labangabadlezane!</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 13:18"/><char style="wj">Khulekani ukuthi lokhu kungenzakali ebusika,</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 13:19"/><char style="wj">ngoba lezo zizakuba yizinsuku zokuhlukuluzeka okungakaze kube khona kwasekuqaleni, lapho uNkulunkulu adala umhlaba, kuze kube manje, njalo kakuzukubuye kube khona.</char><verse eid="MRK 13:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 13:20"/>
    <char style="wj">Nxa iNkosi yayingaziphungulanga lezinsuku, kwakungeyi kuphepha muntu. Kodwa ngenxa yabakhethiweyo, eyabakhethayo, iziphungulile.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 13:21"/><char style="wj">Ngalesosikhathi nxa umuntu esithi kini, ‘Khangelani, nangu uKhristu!’ loba ‘Khangelani, nanguya,’ lingamkholwa.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 13:22"/><char style="wj">Ngoba oKhristu bamanga labaphrofethi bamanga bazavela benze izibonakaliso lezimangaliso ukukhohlisa abakhethiweyo, nxa lokho kungenzeka.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 13:23"/><char style="wj">Ngakho lilimuke; sengilitshelile konke ngaphambili.</char><verse eid="MRK 13:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 13:24"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa ngalezonsuku, kulandela lokho kuhlukuluzeka,</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 13:24">
    <char style="wj">‘ilanga lizafiphala,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 13:24">
    <char style="wj">lenyanga kayiyikukhanya;</char><verse eid="MRK 13:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 13:25"/>
    <char style="wj">izinkanyezi zizakuwa esibhakabhakeni,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 13:25">
    <char style="wj">lezisekelo zasezulwini zizazanyazanyiswa.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">13.25 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 13.10; 34.4</char>
    </note><verse eid="MRK 13:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 13:26"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngalesosikhathi abantu bazayibona iNdodana yoMuntu isiza emayezini ilamandla amakhulu lobukhosi.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 13:27"/><char style="wj">Izathuma izingilosi zayo ziqoqe abakhethiweyo bayo kumagumbi womane omhlaba, kusukela emikhawulweni yomhlaba kusiya emikhawulweni yamazulu.</char><verse eid="MRK 13:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 13:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Manje-ke, fundani lesisifundo esihlahleni somkhiwa: Amahlumela aso angaqalisa ukuba buthakathaka lamahlamvu aso ahlume, lihle lazi ukuthi ihlobo selisondele.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 13:29"/><char style="wj">Kanjalo-ke nxa lingabona lezizinto sezisenzakala, lazi ukuthi sekusondele, khonapho emnyango.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 13:30"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso, lesisizukulwane kasiyikudlula zize zenzakale zonke lezizinto.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 13:31"/><char style="wj">Izulu lomhlaba kuzedlula, kodwa amazwi ami kawayikwedlula lanini.”</char><verse eid="MRK 13:31"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Usuku Lesikhathi Kakwaziwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 13:32"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kodwa kakho olwaziyo lolosuku lehola, loba izingilosi zasezulwini, kumbe iNdodana, kodwa uBaba kuphela.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 13:33"/><char style="wj">Lindani! Qaphelani! Kalikwazi ukuthi sizafika nini lesosikhathi.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 13:34"/><char style="wj">Kunjengomuntu ezathatha uhambo: utshiya indlu yakhe ayinikele izisebenzi zakhe ukuba ziyilinde, yileso sabelwe owaso umsebenzi, atshele lowo olinda emnyango ukuthi aqaphele.</char><verse eid="MRK 13:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 13:35"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho lindani ngoba kalikwazi ukuthi umninindlu uzabuya nini, mhlawumbe kusihlwa, kumbe phakathi kwamabili, loba inkukhu sezikhala kumbe emathathakusa.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 13:36"/><char style="wj">Nxa efika masinyane, akangalifici lilele.</char> <verse eid="MRK 13:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 13:37"/><char style="wj">Engikutshoyo kini ngikutsho emuntwini wonke: ‘Lindani!’ ”</char><verse eid="MRK 13:37"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 13"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c" sid="MRK 14"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uyagcotshwa EBhethani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 14:1"/>Kwasekusele insuku ezimbili kuphela ukuba ufike uMkhosi wePhasika loMkhosi weSinkwa esingelaMvubelo. Abaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho babedinga indlela ecatshileyo yokubopha uJesu ukuze bambulale. <verse eid="MRK 14:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 14:2"/>Kodwa bathi, “Kakungabi ngesikhathi somkhosi, funa abantu benze isiphithiphithi.”<verse eid="MRK 14:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 14:3"/>Kwathi eseBhethani eyeme etafuleni emzini wendoda eyayithiwa nguSimoni owayelobulephero, owesifazane weza ephethe imbodlela yamakha adulayo kakhulu, enziwe ngenadi elipheleleyo. Wayivula imbodlela wathela amakha ekhanda likaJesu.<verse eid="MRK 14:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 14:4"/>Abanye balabo ababekhona bacaphuka babuzana bathi, “Udlaliselani amakha la? <verse eid="MRK 14:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 14:5"/>Abengathengiswa ngokudlula umholo womnyaka wonke imali leyo iphiwe abampofu.” Bamkhuza ngokumkhahlameza kakhulu.<verse eid="MRK 14:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 14:6"/>UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Myekeleni. Limkhathazelani kanti? Wenze into enhle kimi.</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 14:7"/><char style="wj">Abampofu lizahlala lilabo, yikho lingabasiza noma yisiphi isikhathi elisifunayo. Kodwa kalisoze libe lami kokuphela.</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 14:8"/><char style="wj">Wenze lokho abe lamandla okukwenza. Uthele amakha emzimbeni wami mandulo ukulungisela ukungcwatshwa kwami.</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 14:9"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi loba kungaphi okuzatshunyayelwa ivangeli emhlabeni wonke, lokho akwenzileyo kuzakhulunywa, kube yisikhumbuzo ngaye.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 14:10"/>Yikho uJudasi Iskariyothi, omunye wabalitshumi lambili waya kubaphristi abakhulu ukuyanikela uJesu kubo. <verse eid="MRK 14:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 14:11"/>Bathokoza kakhulu bekuzwa lokhu, bathembisa ukumupha imali. Yikho walindela ithuba lokumnikela.<verse eid="MRK 14:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isidlo SeNkosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 14:12"/>Ngelanga lokuqala loMkhosi weSinkwa esingelaMvubelo, lapho kwakungumkhuba ukwenza umhlatshelo wezinyane lePhasika, abafundi bakaJesu bambuza bathi, “Ufuna ukuthi seyekwenza ngaphi amalungiselelo okuthi udle iPhasika na?”<verse eid="MRK 14:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 14:13"/>Ngakho wathuma ababili kubafundi bakhe wabatshela wathi, <char style="wj">“Yanini edolobheni, kuzakuthi indoda ezabe ithwele isigubhu samanzi izalihlangabeza. Ilandeleni.</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 14:14"/><char style="wj">Libokuthi kumninindlu ezangena kuyo, ‘UMfundisi uyabuza uthi: Ingaphi indlu yezethekeli lapho engingadlela khona iPhasika labafundi bami?’</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 14:15"/><char style="wj">Izalitshengisa ikamelo laphezulu elikhulu, elilungisiweyo. Senzeleni amalungiselelo khonapho.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 14:16"/>Abafundi basuka baya edolobheni bafica izinto zimi njengoba uJesu wayetshilo. Yikho basebelungisela iPhasika.<verse eid="MRK 14:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 14:17"/>Kwathi kusihlwa uJesu wafika labalitshumi lambili. <verse eid="MRK 14:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 14:18"/>Bathi beyeme etafuleni besidla wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi omunye wenu uzanginikela, odla lami khonapha.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 14:19"/>Badana, bathi kuye ngamunye, “Pho kawutsho mina?”<verse eid="MRK 14:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 14:20"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngomunye wabalitshumi lambili, omunye otsheba lami isinkwa emganwini.</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 14:21"/><char style="wj">Indodana yoMuntu izahamba njengokulotshiweyo ngayo. Kodwa maye kuleyondoda enikela iNdodana yoMuntu! Kwakungaba ngcono kuyo aluba yayingazalwanga.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 14:22"/>Bathi belokhu besidla uJesu wathatha isinkwa, wabonga, wasihlephula, wasipha abafundi bakhe esithi, <char style="wj">“Sithatheni; lo ngumzimba wami.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 14:23"/>Wasethatha inkezo, esebongile, wabanika, bonke banatha kuyo.<verse eid="MRK 14:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 14:24"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Leli ligazi lami lesivumelwano, elichithelwa abanengi.</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 14:25"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi angisayikuphinda nginathe okwesithelo sevini njalo, kuze kube yilolosuku lapho engizakunatha khona kabutsha embusweni kaNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 14:26"/>Bathi sebehlabele ihubo, baphuma baya eNtabeni yama-Oliva.<verse eid="MRK 14:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ubonisa Ngokuphika KukaPhethro</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 14:27"/>UJesu wabatshela wathi, <char style="wj">“Lonke lizachitheka, ngoba kulotshiwe ukuthi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MRK 14:27">
    <char style="wj">‘Ngizatshaya umelusi,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MRK 14:27">
    <char style="wj">izimvu zihlakazeke.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">14.27 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">UZakhariya 13.7</char>
    </note><verse eid="MRK 14:27"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 14:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa ngemva kokuba sengivukile kwabafileyo, ngizalandulela ukuya eGalile.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 14:29"/>UPhethro walandula wathi, “Loba bonke bengahlakazeka, mina kangisoze ngikwenze.”<verse eid="MRK 14:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 14:30"/>UJesu wamphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngikutshela iqiniso ukuthi lamuhla lokhu, ngobusuku balamuhla, iqhude lingakakhali kabili, wena ngokwakho uzangiphika kathathu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 14:31"/>Kodwa uPhethro waphika wagomela wathi, “Loba kungabe ngifanele ngife lawe, kangisoze ngikuphike.” Bonke abanye labo batsho khona lokho.<verse eid="MRK 14:31"/></para>
  <para style="s1">EGetsemane</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 14:32"/>Baya endaweni eyayithiwa yiGetsemane, uJesu wathi kubafundi bakhe, <char style="wj">“Hlalani lapha mina ngisayakhuleka.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 14:33"/>Wathatha uPhethro, uJakhobe loJohane wasuduluka labo, waseqala ukuhlulukelwa kakhulu lokukhathazeka. <verse eid="MRK 14:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 14:34"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Umphefumulo wami udabukile kakhulu kuze kuthi ngife. Hlalani lapha lilinde.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 14:35"/>Wahamba ibanganyana, wazilahla phansi wakhuleka ukuthi aluba kungenzeka lelohola lingedlula kuye. <verse eid="MRK 14:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 14:36"/>Wathi, <char style="wj">“<char style="tl">Abha,</char> Baba, konke kuyeneliseka kuwe. Ake ususe inkezo le kimi. Kodwa kakungabi yintando yami, kodwa kube yintando yakho.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 14:37"/>Wasephenduka kubafundi bakhe wabafica belele. Wathi kuPhethro, <char style="wj">“Simoni, ulele? Wehlulekile ukulinda ihola elilodwa kuphela?</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 14:38"/><char style="wj">Lindani likhuleke ukuze lingaweli ekulingweni. Umoya uyathanda, kodwa umzimba ubuthakathaka.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 14:39"/>Waphinda wahamba wayakhuleka umkhuleko munye. <verse eid="MRK 14:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 14:40"/>Wathi ekubuyeni wabafica njalo sebelele, ngoba ubuthongo babubaphethe. Baswela ukuthi bathini kuye.<verse eid="MRK 14:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 14:41"/>Esebuya okwesithathu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Lilokhu lilele liphumula? Sekwanele! Isikhathi sesifikile. Khangelani, iNdodana yoMuntu isinikelwe ezandleni zezoni.</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 14:42"/><char style="wj">Phakamani! Kasihambeni! Nangu usesiza onginikelayo.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:42"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubotshwa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="MRK 14:43"/>Esakhuluma, uJudasi, omunye wabalitshumi lambili, wafika. Wayehamba lexuku behlomile ngezinkemba lezinduku, bethunyiwe ngabaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho kanye labadala.<verse eid="MRK 14:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="MRK 14:44"/>Umthengisi wayelungise isiboniso sokubatshengisa wathi: “Lowo engizamanga nguye; limbophe lihle lihambe laye elindiwe.” <verse eid="MRK 14:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="MRK 14:45"/>UJudasi wahle waqonda kuJesu wathi, “Rabi!” wamanga. <verse eid="MRK 14:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MRK 14:46"/>Amadoda ahle amdumela uJesu ambopha. <verse eid="MRK 14:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="MRK 14:47"/>Kwasekusithi omunye owayemi khonapho wakhokha inkemba yakhe wagalela inceku yomphristi omkhulu wayiquma indlebe yayo.<verse eid="MRK 14:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="MRK 14:48"/>UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngingumkhokheli womvukela yini, selingaze lize lihlomile ngezinkemba lezinduku ukuzangibamba?</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="MRK 14:49"/><char style="wj">Bengilani insuku zonke ngifundisa emagumeni ethempeli, kodwa kalingibophanga. Kodwa iMibhalo kufanele igcwaliseke.”</char> <verse eid="MRK 14:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="MRK 14:50"/>Khonokho bonke bamtshiya babaleka.<verse eid="MRK 14:50"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="MRK 14:51"/>Ijaha elalingagqokanga lutho ngaphandle kwelembu lelineni lalimlandela uJesu. Balibamba, <verse eid="MRK 14:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="MRK 14:52"/>kodwa labaleka laze latshiya isembatho salo.<verse eid="MRK 14:52"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Phambi KoMphakathi ISanihedrini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v" sid="MRK 14:53"/>UJesu bamthatha bamusa kumphristi omkhulu, kwathi bonke abaphristi abakhulu, labadala labafundisi bomthetho babuthana ndawonye. <verse eid="MRK 14:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="MRK 14:54"/>UPhethro wamlandela ehambela khatshana, waze wayangena egumeni lomphristi omkhulu. Wahlala khonapho labalindi esotha umlilo.<verse eid="MRK 14:54"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="55" style="v" sid="MRK 14:55"/>Abaphristi abakhulu leSanihedrini yonke babedinga ubufakazi obumlahlayo uJesu ukuze bambulale, kodwa babuswela. <verse eid="MRK 14:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="MRK 14:56"/>Abanengi bafakaza amanga ngaye, kodwa amazwi abo kawavumelananga.<verse eid="MRK 14:56"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v" sid="MRK 14:57"/>Kwasekusukuma abanye bethula lobu ubufakazi bamanga ngaye, bathi, <verse eid="MRK 14:57"/><verse number="58" style="v" sid="MRK 14:58"/>“Samuzwa esithi, ‘Ngizalibhidliza ithempeli leli, elakhiwe ngabantu ngakhe elinye ngezinsuku ezintathu, elizabe lingasakhiwanga ngumuntu.’ ” <verse eid="MRK 14:58"/><verse number="59" style="v" sid="MRK 14:59"/>Lakulokhu kabuvumelananga ubufakazi babo.<verse eid="MRK 14:59"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="60" style="v" sid="MRK 14:60"/>Umphristi omkhulu wasesukuma phambi kwabo wabuza uJesu wathi, “Kawuyikuphendula na? Kuyini kanti lokhu okufakazwa ngamadoda la ngawe na?” <verse eid="MRK 14:60"/><verse number="61" style="v" sid="MRK 14:61"/>Kodwa uJesu wala elokhu ethule njalo kazange aphendule.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 14:61">Umphristi omkhulu waphinde wambuza wathi, “Unguye uKhristu, iNdodana yoBusisiweyo na?”<verse eid="MRK 14:61"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="62" style="v" sid="MRK 14:62"/>UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Nginguye. Njalo lizayibona iNdodana yoMuntu ihlezi kwesokunene salowo Olamandla isehla ngamayezi ezulu.”</char><verse eid="MRK 14:62"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="63" style="v" sid="MRK 14:63"/>Umphristi omkhulu wadabula izigqoko zakhe wabuza wathi, “Sisabadingelani abanye ofakazi? <verse eid="MRK 14:63"/><verse number="64" style="v" sid="MRK 14:64"/>Selikuzwile ukuhlambaza. Lithini manje?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 14:64">Bonke bamlahla bathi ufanele ukufa. <verse eid="MRK 14:64"/><verse number="65" style="v" sid="MRK 14:65"/>Abanye basebeqalisa ukumkhafulela; bamvala amehlo ngokumbopha, bamdutshuza ngenqindi bathi, “Phrofitha!” Abalindi basebemthatha bayamtshaya.<verse eid="MRK 14:65"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhethro Ulandula UJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="66" style="v" sid="MRK 14:66"/>UPhethro wayengaphansi egumeni, enye yamantombazana ayeyizincekukazi zomphristi omkhulu yeza khonapho. <verse eid="MRK 14:66"/><verse number="67" style="v" sid="MRK 14:67"/>Yathi ibona uPhethro esotha umlilo yamkhangelisisa.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 14:67">Yathi, “Lawe wawulomNazarini lowaya, uJesu.”<verse eid="MRK 14:67"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="68" style="v" sid="MRK 14:68"/>Walandula. Wathi, “Angikwazi njalo kangikuzwisisi lokho okhuluma ngakho.” Wahle waphuma waya esangweni.<verse eid="MRK 14:68"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="69" style="v" sid="MRK 14:69"/>Kuthe intombazana leyo isimbona khona lapho yathi kwababemi lapho, “Indoda le ingomunye wabo.” <verse eid="MRK 14:69"/><verse number="70" style="v" sid="MRK 14:70"/>Walandula njalo.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 14:70">Ngemva kwesikhatshana ababemi lapho eduze kukaPhethro bathi, “Ngeqiniso ungomunye wabo, ngoba ungumGalile.”<verse eid="MRK 14:70"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="71" style="v" sid="MRK 14:71"/>Watshinga uPhethro, waziqalekisa wabuye wafunga kubo wathi, “Kangiyazi indoda le elikhuluma ngayo.”<verse eid="MRK 14:71"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="72" style="v" sid="MRK 14:72"/>Masinyane lakhala iqhude ngokwesibili. Khonapho uPhethro waselikhumbula ilizwi uJesu ayelitshilo kuye, ukuthi: <char style="wj">“Iqhude lingakakhali kabili uzangiphika kathathu.”</char> Ngakho waphihlika wakhala.<verse eid="MRK 14:72"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 14"/>
  <chapter number="15" style="c" sid="MRK 15"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ephambi KukaPhilathu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 15:1"/>Ekuseni kakhulu abaphristi abakhulu, labadala, labafundisi bomthetho kanye leSanihedrini yonke bavumelana ngesinqumo sabo. Bambopha uJesu bamqhuba bayamethula kuPhilathu.<verse eid="MRK 15:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 15:2"/>UPhilathu wambuza wathi, “Uyinkosi yamaJuda na?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 15:2">UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Usukutshilo lokho.”</char><verse eid="MRK 15:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 15:3"/>Abaphristi abakhulu bamethesa amacala amanengi. <verse eid="MRK 15:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 15:4"/>Ngakho uPhilathu wambuza njalo wathi, “Kanti kungani ungaphenduli na? Khangela, bakubeka amacala amanengi.”<verse eid="MRK 15:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 15:5"/>Kodwa uJesu wala elokhu ethule, uPhilathu wamangala.<verse eid="MRK 15:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 15:6"/>Kwakungumkhuba ukuthi ngomkhosi kukhululwe isibotshwa esasizabe sicelwe ngabantu. <verse eid="MRK 15:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 15:7"/>Indoda eyayithiwa nguBharabhasi yayisentolongweni kanye labahlamuki ababebulele abantu kulowomvukela. <verse eid="MRK 15:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 15:8"/>Ixuku labantu leza kuPhilathu ukuthi abenzele leyo nhlalayenza.<verse eid="MRK 15:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 15:9"/>“Lifuna ukuthi ngilikhululele inkosi yamaJuda na?” UPhilathu wabuza, <verse eid="MRK 15:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 15:10"/>esazi ukuthi kwakungenxa yomhawu okwenza abaphristi abakhulu banikela uJesu kuye. <verse eid="MRK 15:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 15:11"/>Kodwa abaphristi abakhulu badunga abantu babakhuthaza ukuthi bacele uPhilathu abakhululele uBharabhasi.<verse eid="MRK 15:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 15:12"/>UPhilathu wasebabuza wathi, “Pho ngithini ngalo elimbiza ngokuthi uyinkosi yamaJuda na?”<verse eid="MRK 15:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 15:13"/>Bamemeza bathi, “Mbethele!”<verse eid="MRK 15:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 15:14"/>UPhilathu wabuza wathi, “Yindaba? Woneni?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 15:14">Kodwa bamemeza ngamandla bathi, “Mbethele!”<verse eid="MRK 15:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 15:15"/>UPhilathu wasebakhululela uBharabhasi ngoba wayefuna ukusuthisa ixuku labantu. Wathi uJesu katshaywe, ngemva kwalokho wasebapha ukuba bambethele.<verse eid="MRK 15:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amabutho Ahoza UJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 15:16"/>Amabutho amqhuba uJesu amusa esigodlweni (kutshiwo iPhrethoriyamu) basebebiza iviyo lonke lamabutho laqoqana ndawonye. <verse eid="MRK 15:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 15:17"/>Bamgqokisa ijazi eliyibubende, basebeseluka umqhele wameva bamethesa wona. <verse eid="MRK 15:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 15:18"/>Basebememeza besithi kuye, “Bayethe, nkosi yamaJuda!” <verse eid="MRK 15:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 15:19"/>Bamtshaya ekhanda ngomqwayi baphindaphinda, bamkhafulela. Baguqa phansi ngamadolo bamkhonza. <verse eid="MRK 15:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 15:20"/>Sebemhozile, bamhlubula ijazi eliyibubende bamgqokisa ezakhe izigqoko. Basebephuma laye bamqhuba ukuba bayombethela.<verse eid="MRK 15:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubethelwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MRK 15:21"/>Indoda ethile yaseKhureni, eyayithiwa nguSimoni, uyise ka-Alekizanda loRufasi, wayezedlulela khonapho evela emaphandleni, basebembamba ngamandla ukuthi athwale isiphambano. <verse eid="MRK 15:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MRK 15:22"/>Baletha uJesu endaweni eyayithiwa yiGoligotha (okutsho ukuthi, “Indawo yoKhakhayi”). <verse eid="MRK 15:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MRK 15:23"/>Basebemupha iwayini elihlanganiswe lemure, kodwa wala ukulinatha. <verse eid="MRK 15:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MRK 15:24"/>Basebembethela. Bahlukanisa izigqoko zakhe basebesenza inkatho ukuze babone ukuthi ngulowo athathe kuphi.<verse eid="MRK 15:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MRK 15:25"/>Kwakulihola lesithathu isikhathi abambethela ngaso. <verse eid="MRK 15:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MRK 15:26"/>Umbhalo wecala lakhe wawusithi:</para>
  <para style="pc" vid="MRK 15:26">INkosi yamaJuda.<verse eid="MRK 15:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MRK 15:27"/>Babethela kanye laye abaphangi ababili, omunye kwesokunene sakhe, omunye kwesokhohlo. [ <verse eid="MRK 15:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MRK 15:28"/>Kwagcwaliseka umbhalo othi, “Wabalwa ndawonye lezephulamthetho.”]<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.28 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi ayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note> <verse eid="MRK 15:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MRK 15:29"/>Labo ababedlula lapho babemthuka benikina amakhanda abo besithi, “Ehe! Wena ozadiliza ithempeli ulakhe ngezinsuku ezintathu, <verse eid="MRK 15:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MRK 15:30"/>yehla esiphambanweni uzisindise!” <verse eid="MRK 15:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MRK 15:31"/>Ngaleyondlela labaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho bamklolodela behlekisana ngaye phakathi kwabo. Bathi, “Wasindisa abanye, kodwa uyehluleka ukuzisindisa yena! <verse eid="MRK 15:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MRK 15:32"/>Ake kuthi uKhristu lo, iNkosi le yako-Israyeli, yehle esiphambanweni ukuze sibone, sikholwe.” Lalabo ayebethelwe kanye labo, labo babemhlambaza.<verse eid="MRK 15:32"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukufa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MRK 15:33"/>Ngehola lesithupha ubumnyama bembesa ilizwe lonke kwaze kwaba lihola lesificamunwemunye. <verse eid="MRK 15:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MRK 15:34"/>Kwathi ngehola lesithathu emini uJesu wakhala ngelizwi elikhulu wathi, <char style="tl"><char style="wj">“Eloyi, Eloyi, lamasabakithani?”</char></char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.34 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 22.1</char></note> (okutsho ukuthi, <char style="wj">“Nkulunkulu wami, Nkulunkulu wami, ungitshiyelani na?”</char>).<verse eid="MRK 15:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MRK 15:35"/>Kwathi abanye balabo ababemi eduzane bekuzwa lokho bathi, “Zwanini, ubiza u-Elija.”<verse eid="MRK 15:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MRK 15:36"/>Enye indoda yagcwalisa uzipho ngewayini elimunyu, yaluxhumela oluthini, yasiluqhubela uJesu ukuthi anathe. Yasisithi, “Ake simyekele manje, kesibone ingabe u-Elija uzakuza azomehlisa.”<verse eid="MRK 15:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MRK 15:37"/>Ngomkhosi omkhulu, uJesu waphefumula okokucina.<verse eid="MRK 15:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MRK 15:38"/>Ikhetheni lethempeli ladabuka kabili lisuka phezulu kusiya phansi. <verse eid="MRK 15:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MRK 15:39"/>Kwathi induna yekhulu eyayimi khonapho phambi kukaJesu isizwa ukukhala kwakhe njalo ikubonile ukuthi ufe kanjani yathi, “Ngeqiniso indoda le ibe iyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu!”<verse eid="MRK 15:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="MRK 15:40"/>Abanye abesifazane babebukele bebucwala. Phakathi kwabo kwakuloMariya Magadalini loMariya unina kaJakhobe omncinyane lokaJosefa loSalome. <verse eid="MRK 15:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MRK 15:41"/>Laba abesifazane babemlandele bemsebenzela eseGalile. Labanye abesifazane abanengi ababeze laye eJerusalema labo babekhona.<verse eid="MRK 15:41"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukungcwatshwa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="MRK 15:42"/>Kwakulusuku lokuLungiselela (kutsho usuku olwandulela iSabatha). Kwathi sekuntambama <verse eid="MRK 15:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="MRK 15:43"/>uJosefa wase-Arimathiya indoda elesithunzi eNkundleni, yona ngokwayo eyayilindele umbuso kaNkulunkulu, yaqunga isibindi yaya kuPhilathu yacela isidumbu sikaJesu. <verse eid="MRK 15:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MRK 15:44"/>UPhilathu wamangala ukuthi wayesefile. Wabiza induna yekhulu wayibuza ukuthi uJesu wayesefile yini. <verse eid="MRK 15:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="MRK 15:45"/>Wathi esezwile ngenduna yekhulu ukuthi kwasekwenzakele, wamupha uJosefa isidumbu. <verse eid="MRK 15:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MRK 15:46"/>Ngakho uJosefa wasethenga amalembu elineni, wathatha isidumbu wasigoqela ngelineni wasibeka ethuneni elaligujwe edwaleni. Wasegiqela ilitshe emlonyeni wethuna. <verse eid="MRK 15:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="MRK 15:47"/>UMariya Magadalini loMariya unina kaJosefa babona lapho abekwa khona.<verse eid="MRK 15:47"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 15"/>
  <chapter number="16" style="c" sid="MRK 16"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuvuka KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MRK 16:1"/>Kwathi iSabatha seledlule, uMariya Magadalini, loMariya unina kaJakhobe loSalome bathenga amakha ukuze bayeqhola ngawo isidumbu sikaJesu. <verse eid="MRK 16:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MRK 16:2"/>Ekuseni kakhulu ngosuku lokuqala lweviki, ilanga liphuma basebesendleleni besiya ethuneni, <verse eid="MRK 16:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MRK 16:3"/>babuzana bathi, “Ngubani ozasigiqela ilitshe lisuke emlonyeni wethuna na?”<verse eid="MRK 16:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MRK 16:4"/>Kodwa bathi bayakhangela babona ilitshe, elalilikhulu kakhulu, seligiqelwe eceleni. <verse eid="MRK 16:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MRK 16:5"/>Bathi bengena ethuneni babona ijaha ligqoke isembatho esimhlophe lihlezi ngakwesokunene, bethuka kakhulu.<verse eid="MRK 16:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MRK 16:6"/>Lathi, “Lingaze lethuka. Lidinga uJesu umNazarini obebethelwe. Usevukile! Kakho lapha. Bonani, nansi indawo lapho bebembeke khona. <verse eid="MRK 16:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MRK 16:7"/>Kodwa hambani liyotshela abafundi bakhe loPhethro lithi, ‘Usehamba phambi kwenu ukuya eGalile. Lizambona khonale, njengoba walitshela.’ ”<verse eid="MRK 16:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MRK 16:8"/>Ngokuthuthumela langokudideka, abesifazane baphuma bebaleka ethuneni. Kabakhulumanga lutho lakubani ngoba babesesaba.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">16.8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Eminye imibhalo iphetha ngovesi 8 lo 9 njalo umbhalo owodwa ulovesi 8 (kodwa weqa uvesi 9‑20): </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">Ngakho baphanga babika zonke izeluleko lezo kuPhethro labanye ayelabo. Emva kwalokho uJesu ngokwakhe wabathuma ukuyatshumayela ivangeli elingcwele lelingapheliyo njalo elilensindiso yaphakade kusuka empumalanga kusiya entshonalanga. Amen.</char></note></para>
  <para style="b" vid="MRK 16:8"/>
  <para style="p" vid="MRK 16:8">[ <verse eid="MRK 16:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MRK 16:9"/>UJesu esevukile ekuseni ngelanga lokuqala evikini waqala wabonakala kuMariya Magadalini yena lowo ayekhuphe kuye amadimoni ayisikhombisa. <verse eid="MRK 16:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MRK 16:10"/>Yena wahamba wayabikela labo uJesu ayephile labo ababesesililweni sakhe. <verse eid="MRK 16:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MRK 16:11"/>Bathi besizwa ukuthi uJesu uyaphila lokuthi uMariya wayembonile, kabazange bakukholwe.<verse eid="MRK 16:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MRK 16:12"/>Ngemva kwalokho uJesu wabonakala ngesinye isimo kwababili babo abafica behamba kulelolizwe emaphandleni. <verse eid="MRK 16:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MRK 16:13"/>Labo babuyela bayabikela abanye, kodwa labo kabazange babakholwe.<verse eid="MRK 16:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MRK 16:14"/>Ngemva kwalokho uJesu wabonakala kwabalitshumi lanye besidla; wabakhuza ngokungakholwa kwabo langobulukhuni benhliziyo zabo bengabakholwa labo ababembonile ngemva kokuvuka kwakhe.<verse eid="MRK 16:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MRK 16:15"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Hambani emhlabeni wonke litshumayele ivangeli kukho konke okwadalwayo.</char> <verse eid="MRK 16:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MRK 16:16"/><char style="wj">Loba ngubani okholwayo abhaphathizwe uzasindiswa, kodwa lowo ongakholwayo uzalahlwa.</char> <verse eid="MRK 16:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MRK 16:17"/><char style="wj">Lezizibonakaliso zizabalandela labo abakholwayo: Ngebizo lami bazakhupha amadimoni; bazakhuluma ngendimi ezintsha;</char> <verse eid="MRK 16:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MRK 16:18"/><char style="wj">bazadobha izinyoka ngezandla zabo; bazakuthi banganatha okubulalayo kungaze kwabalimaza lakancinyane; bazabeka izandla zabo phezu kwabantu abagulayo, basile.”</char><verse eid="MRK 16:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MRK 16:19"/>Ngemva kokuba iNkosi uJesu esekhulume labo, wenyukiselwa ezulwini, wahlala ngakwesokunene sikaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="MRK 16:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MRK 16:20"/>Abafundi bahamba bayatshumayela ezindaweni zonke iNkosi yasebenza labo yaqinisa ilizwi layo ngezibonakaliso ezazilisekela.]<verse eid="MRK 16:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MRK 16"/>
</usx>
